d%20Of%20Farmers'%20March%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESecurity%20has%20been%20intensified%20along%20the%20Singhu%2C%20Ghazipur%20and%20Tikri%20borders%20to%20stop%20farmers'%20mega%20protest%20in%20Delhi%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20barricades%20have%20already%20been%20installed%20at%20the%20borders%20to%20stop%20the%20farmers%20from%20entering%20the%20national%20capital.%20Nails%20have%20been%20erected%20on%20roads%20so%20that%20if%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20try%20to%20enter%20the%20city%20on%20vehicles%2C%20their%20tyres%20can%20be%20punctured%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20many%20as%201%2C000%20to%201%2C500%20Delhi%20Police%20personnel%20will%20be%20deployed%20in%20each%20of%20these%20border%20areas.%20However%2C%20the%20pattern%20of%20deployment%20and%20the%20number%20of%20personnel%20will%20change%20as%20per%20the%20situation%20in%20these%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20police%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20teams%20have%20been%20formed%20to%20keep%20strict%20vigil%20on%20bus%20stands%2C%20metro%20stations%2C%20railway%20stations%20and%20roads%20to%20ensure%20that%20farmers%20do%20not%20enter%20the%20city%20using%20any%20other%20mode%20of%20conveyance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborate%20arrangements%20have%20been%20made%20to%20seal%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20borders%20in%20Ambala%2C%20Jind%2C%20and%20Fatehabad%20districts.The%20Haryana%20government%20has%20also%20ordered%20the%20suspension%20of%20mobile%20internet%20services%20and%20bulk%20SMS%20in%20seven%20districts%20-%20Ambala%2C%20Kurukshetra%2C%20Kaithal%2C%20Jind%2C%20Hisar%2C%20Fatehabad%20and%20Sirsa%20-%20ahead%20of%20the%20farmers'%20proposed%20march.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELarge%20gatherings%20have%20been%20banned%20in%20all%20areas%20along%20the%20UP%20border%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20North-East%20district%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20even%20as%20the%20farmers%20are%20readying%20their%20tractor%20trolleys%20to%20par