t%3BIt%20means%20a%20ton%2C%26quot%3B%20Mahomes%20said.%20%26quot%3BWith%20the%20adversity%20we%20dealt%20with%20this%20year%20and%20to%20come%20through%2C%20the%20guys%20never%20faltered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahomes%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20warned%20the%20Chiefs'%20rivals%20that%20their%20latest%20win%20was%20just%20the%20start%20of%20their%20dynasty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20a%20young%20team.%20We're%20going%20to%20keep%20this%20thing%20going.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20long%20periods%2C%20however%2C%20it%20looked%20as%20if%20Kansas%20City%20would%20be%20denied%20by%20San%20Francisco's%20ferocious%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChiefs%20star%20Travis%20Kelce%20--%20the%20boyfriend%20of%20watching%20singer%20Swift%20--%20had%20a%20nightmare%20start%20to%20the%20game%2C%20at%20one%20stage%20blowing%20up%20on%20the%20sidelines%20at%20Kansas%20City%20head%20coach%20Andy%20Reid%20in%20an%20extraordinary%20outburst.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20Mahomes%20pulling%20the%20strings%2C%20the%20Chiefs%20finally%20battled%20through%20a%20below-par%20performance%20to%20deliver%20when%20it%20mattered%20once%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20marked%20the%20third%20time%20that%20Mahomes%20has%20led%20Kansas%20City%20back%20from%20double-digit%20deficits%20to%20win%20the%20Super%20Bowl%2C%20sealing%20his%20reputation%20as%20the%20heir%20apparent%20to%20the%20legendary%20Tom%20Brady.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chiefs%20fell%20behind%2010-0%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20after%20San%20Francisco%20struck%20first%20through%20a%2055-yard%20Jake%20Moody%20field%20goal%20and%20a%20brilliantly%20worked%20trick%20play%20that%20ended%20with%20a%20touchdown%20for%20running%20back%20Christian%20McCaffrey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKansas%20City%20were%20left%20with%20just%20a%20Harrison%20Butker%20field%20goal%20to%20show%20for%20their%20first%20half%20efforts%20to%20make%20it%2010-3%20at%20the%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKelce%20meltdown%2C%20overtime%20drama%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKelce%20went%20berserk%20on%20the%20Chiefs%20bench%2C%20with%20the%20tight%20end%20screaming%20at%20head%20coach%20Andy%20Reid%20in%20apparent%20frustration%20at%20being%20kept%20off%20the%20field%20for%20the%20play%20when%20an%20early%20Kansas%20City%20drive%20ended%20with%20an%20Isiah%20Pacheco%20fumble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKansas%20City's%20offense%20fared%20little%20better%20after%20the%20restart%2C%20with%20Mahomes%20giving%20up%20an%20interception%20to%2049ers%20safety%20Ji'ayir%20Brown%20after%20an%20overthrown%20pass%20intended%20for%20Marquez%20Valdes-Scantling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESan%20Francisco%20were%20unable%20to%20turn%20the%20possession%20into%20points%2C%20however%2C%20as%20defenses%20stayed%20on%20top%2C%20forcing%20punts%20on%20the%20next%20three%20possessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKansas%20City%20added%20to%20their%20tally%20with%20a%20monstrous%2057-yard%20Butker%20field%20goal%20that%20crept%20over%20the%20bar%20to%20eclipse%20Moody's%20record-long%20first-half%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20San%20Francisco's%20defense%20still%20on%20top%2C%20Kansas%20City%20needed%20a%20stroke%20of%20luck%20and%20they%20got%20it%20when%20a%20muffed%20punt%20between%2049ers%20defenders%20Darrell%20Luter%20and%20Ray-Ray%20McCloud%20allowed%20the%20Chiefs%20to%20recover%20deep%20in%20the%20red%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahomes%20wasted%20no%20time%20cashing%20in%2C%20hitting%20Valdes%20Scantling%20in%20the%20end%20zone%20from%2016%20yards%2C%20Butker's%20extra%20point%20making%20it%2013-10.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2049ers%20came%20roaring%20back%2C%20however%2C%20on%20the%20next%20drive%2C%20Purdy%20showing%20great%20composure%20to%20lead%20a%2012-play%2075-yard%20touchdown%20drive%20that%20ended%20with%20a%20Jennings%20score.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20potentially%20costly%20missed%20extra%20point%20left%20San%20Francisco%2016-13%20ahead%2C%20and%20the%20Chiefs%20drew%20level%20on%20their%20next%20possession%20with%20Butker's%20third%20field%20goal%20to%20tie%20it%20at%2016-16.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoody%20kicked%20a%2040-yard%20field%20goal%20to%20restore%20San%20Francisco's%20lead%20at%2019-16.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20Mahomes%20to%20lead%20the%20Chiefs%20to%20another%20Super%20Bowl%20comeback%20with%20just%201min%2053sec%20left%20on%20the%20clock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20tension%20mounted%2C%20Mahomes%20found%20Kelce%20for%20a%2023-yard%20gain%20that%20took%20the%20Chiefs%20into%20kicking%20range.%20After%20once%20again%20failing%20to%20get%20the%20ball%20into%20the%20end%20zone%2C%20Butker%20stepped%20up%20to%20level%20it%20at%2019-19%20with%20three%20seconds%20left%2C%20forcing%20overtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESan%20Francisco%20scored%20a%20Moody%20field%20goal%20on%20the%20opening%20possession%20to%20make%20it%2022-19%2C%20but%20Mahomes%20was%20not%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quarterback%20coolly%20marched%20Kansas%20City%20upfield%20to%20the%20three-yard%20line%2C%20and%20then%20popped%20the%20winning%20pass%20to%20Hardman%20to%20seal%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20the%20whole%20game%20was%20our%20whole%20entire%20season%2C%20the%20defense%20just%20keeping%20us%20in%20there%20and%20then%20the%20offense%20making%20plays%20when%20it%20counted%2C%26quot%3B%20Mahomes%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20proud%20of%20the%20guys.%20They%20kept%20believing.%20And%20I'm%20proud%20of%20the%20coaches%20for%20calling%20up%20those%20plays%20that%20got%20us%20some%20touchdowns%20there%20at%20the%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707712860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fulvdqfuo_kansas-city-chiefs-afp_625x300_12_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A