hortly%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20met%20Qatar's%20Amir%20Sheikh%20Tamim%20bin%20Hamad%20Al-Thani%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20COP28%20summit%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20home%2C%20one%20of%20the%20veterans%20thanked%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20very%20happy%20that%20we%20are%20back%20in%20India%2C%20safely.%20Definitely%2C%20we%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20PM%20Modi%20as%20this%20was%20only%20possible%20because%20of%20his%20personal%20intervention.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20waited%20for%2018%20months%20to%20be%20back%20in%20India.%20We%20are%20extremely%20grateful%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20It%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20possible%20without%20his%20personal%20intervention%20and%20his%20equation%20with%20Qatar.%20We%20are%20grateful%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20from%20the%20bottom%20of%20our%20hearts%20for%20every%20effort%20that%20has%20been%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707712500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fek85mn8o_navy-veterans_625x300_12_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnavy-veterans-jailed-in-qatar-navy-veterans-jailed-in-qatar-had-no-clue-they-were-coming-home-sources-5041057%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20seven%20Navy%20veterans%20jailed%20in%20Qatar%2C%20who%20were%20brought%20back%20to%20India%20today%2C%20had%20no%20prior%20information%20of%20their%20release%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnavy-veterans-jailed-in-qatar-navy-veterans-jailed-in-qatar-had-no-clue-they-were-coming-home-sources-5041057%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnavy-veterans-jailed-in-qatar-navy-veterans-jailed-in-qatar-had-no-clue-they-were-coming-home-sources-5041057%2Famp%2F1%