reated%2C%20its%20right%20foot%20in%20a%20cast.%20The%20MP-based%20activist%E2%80%99s%20posts%20claim%20that%20authorities%20%E2%80%98hid%E2%80%99%20this%20development.%20However%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20management%20of%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20have%20rejected%20Dubey%E2%80%99s%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20contacted%20officials%20in%20the%20Forest%20Department%20for%20an%20official%20response%20regarding%20this.%20The%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20once%20they%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECub%20fractured%20foot%2C%20was%20treated%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh-based%20RTI%20activist%20Ajay%20Dubey%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20posts%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%3Ffbid%3D7972895612726175%26set%3Da.896022567080217%5C%22%3EFacebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FAjaydubey9%2Fstatus%2F1755795520218652770%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3ETwitter%3C%2Fa%3E%20(both%20dated%20February%209)%20called%20for%20an%20investigation%20into%20how%20and%20when%20a%20cheetah%20cub%20kept%20in%20a%20closed%20enclosure%20in%20Kuno%20suffered%20from%20a%20foot%20fracture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubey%2C%20in%20his%20social%20media%20posts%2C%20has%20uploaded%20photographs%20of%20an%20official%20correspondence%20dated%20December%205%20from%20the%20Chief%20Conservator%20of%20Forests%20and%20Director%20of%20the%20Lion%20Project%2C%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Sharma%2C%20in%20reply%20to%20an%20inquiry%20from%20the%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority.%20The%20letter%20from%20Sharma%20details%20that%20a%20then%20eight-month-old%20African%20cheetah%20cub%20was%20injured%20on%20November%2028%20last%20year.%20Veterinarians%20treated%20the%20cub%20the%20next%20day%20for%20a%20fracture%20of%20its%20right%20foot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20circumstances%20of%20the%20occurrence%2C%20the%20letter%20says%20that%20recorded%20camera%20footage%20showed%20the%20cub%20%E2%80%93%20apparently%20in%20fine%20health%20then%20%E2%80%93%20running%20after%20treepies%20(a%20bird%20slightly%20larger%20than%20a%20crow)%20in%20its%20enclosure%20at%207%3A54%20am%20and%20then%20disappearing%20behind%20trees.%20It%20emerged%20from%20the%20tree%20clump%20at%208%3A02%20am%20with%20a%20limp.%20Veterinarians%20immobilised%20the%20cub%20and%20treated%20it%20the%20next%20day%2C%20on%20November%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20official%20announcement%20yet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20authorities%20have%20not%20made%20any%20official%20announcement%20on%20the%20alleged%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Dubey%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20posts%20on%20February%209%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FAjaydubey9%2Fstatus%2F1755988018367013072%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Eclaims%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Kuno%20management%20kept%20the%20news%20of%20the%20cub%E2%80%99s%20injury%20from%20the%20NTCA%20for%20several%20days.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbhopal%2Fkuno-cheetah-cub-injured-rti-photo-sparks-row%2Farticleshow%2F107571820.cms%5C%22%3Enews%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20February%2010%20says%20the%20management%20of%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20have%20%E2%80%9Crejected%E2%80%9D%20Dubey%E2%80%99s%20allegations.%20In%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fajay.dubey.564%2Fposts%2Fpfbid02hepeV3jfU3qTtLzHGb61DHnGxZp6M6Dgejg4qU5mCWg5qFHrQ6ZzqKhFRM7C99Enl%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20February%2011%20on%20Facebook%2C%20Dubey%20alleged%20that%20authorities%20hid%20this%20news%2C%20and%20questioned%20why%20they%20did%20so%2C%20suggesting%20that%20an%20investigation%20be%20launched%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20contacted%20officials%20in%20the%20Forest%20Department%20for%20an%20official%20response%20regarding%20an