in%20Valencia%20in%202022%20and%20a%20follow-up%20in%20London%20the%20following%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kenyan%20had%20announced%20he%20would%20attempt%20to%20become%20the%20first%20man%20to%20run%20an%20official%20marathon%20under%20the%20two-hour%20mark%20in%20Rotterdam%20on%20April%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20overwhelming%20favourite%20for%20the%20Paris%202024%20Summer%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorld%20Athletics%20remembered%20Kiptum%20as%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20exciting%20new%20prospects%20to%20emerge%20in%20road%20running%20in%20recent%20years%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20shocked%20and%20deeply%20saddened%20to%20learn%20of%20the%20devastating%20loss%20of%20Kelvin%20Kiptum%20and%20his%20coach%2C%20Gervais%20Hakizimana%2C%26quot%3B%20World%20Athletics%20President%20Sebastian%20Coe%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20behalf%20of%20all%20World%20Athletics%2C%20we%20send%20our%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20their%20families%2C%20friends%2C%20teammates%20and%20the%20Kenyan%20nation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20'Incredible%20athlete'%20-%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnCoe%20said%20only%20last%20week%20he%20had%20been%20in%20Chicago%20%26quot%3Bto%20officially%20ratify%26quot%3B%20Kiptum's%20historic%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20incredible%20athlete%20leaving%20an%20incredible%20legacy%2C%20we%20will%20miss%20him%20dearly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKenyan%20two-time%20Olympic%20800m%20champion%20David%20Rudisha%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bshocked%20and%20deeply%20saddened%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20huge%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAthletics%20Kenya%20extended%20condolences%20to%20%26quot%3Bthe%20entire%20athletics%20community%20during%20this%20difficult%20time%26quot%3B%20while%20Kiptum's%20agent%2C%20Marc%20Corstjens%2C%20also%20c