%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravindra%20Jadeja%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F855-ravindra-jadeja-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20to%20take%20to%20social%20media%20after%20certain%20accusations%20made%20by%20his%20father%20in%20an%20interview%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%20Ravindra's%20father%20claimed%20that%20his%20relationship%20with%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20star%20and%20his%20wife%20Rivaba%20has%20been%20strained%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20prompting%20a%20reply%20from%20the%20all-rounder.%20In%20an%20event%2C%20even%20Ravindra's%20wife%20Rivaba%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20accusations%20by%20her%20husband's%20dad.%20But%2C%20the%20politician%20refused%20to%20dwell%20on%20the%20topic%20and%20reminded%20those%20questioning%20him%20of%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20are%20we%20here%20today%3F%20You%20can%20contact%20me%20directly%20if%20you%20want%20to%20know%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Rivaba%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20comments%20made%20by%20Ravindra's%20father%20in%20a%20video%20shared%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC3Kb5pbJIOR%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dembed_video_watch_again%5C%22%3EZee%2024%20Kalak%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Jadeja%20took%20to%20social%20media%2C%20calling%20the%20interview%20that%20his%20father%20gave%20as%20'meaningless%20and%20false'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20things%20mentioned%20in%20the%20dubious%20interview%20with%20Divya%20Bhaskar%20are%20meaningless%20and%20false.%20Those%20are%20one-sided%20comments%20that%20I%20deny%20them.%20The%20attempt%20to%20tarnish%20the%20image%20of%20my%20wife%20is%20improper%20and%20condemnable.%20I%20too%2C%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20say%20but%20it%20is%20better%20that%20I%20don't%20reveal%20those%20things%20in%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20Jadeja%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20interview%2C%20Ravindra's%20father%20revealed%20how%20his%20son%20and%20daughter-in-law%20live%20separately%20and%20barely%20communicate%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20you%20want%20me%20to%20tell%20you%20one%20truth%3F%20I%20have%20absolutely%20no%20relation%20with%20Ravindra%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Rivaba.%20We%20don't%20call%20them%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20call%20us.%20The%20issues%20started%20after%20two%20or%20three%20months%20of%20their%20marriage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20even%20rued%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20made%20Ravindra%20a%20cricketer.%20Had%20that%20not%20happened%2C%20maybe%20things%20would've%20been%20different%20between%20him%20and%20his%20son%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20currently%20live%20alone%20in%20Jamnagar%2C%20while%20Ravindra%20resides%20in%20a%20separate%20bungalow%20of%20his%20own.%20He%20lives%20in%20the%20same%20city%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20get%20to%20see%20him.%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20magic%20his%20wife%20has%20done%20on%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20my%20son%2C%20and%20it%20burns%20my%20heart.%20I%20wish%20I%20hadn't%20got%20him%20married.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20better%20if%20he%20hadn't%20become%20a%20cricketer.%20We%20would%20not%20have%20to%20go%20through%20all%20this%20in%20that%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20Jadeja's%20father%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithin%20three%20months%20of%20the%20marriage%2C%20she%20told%20me%20that%20everything%20should%20be%20transferred%20to%20her%20name.%20She%20created%20a%20rift%20in%20our%20family.%20She%20didn't%20want%20the%20family%20and%20desired%20an%20independent%20life.%20I%20could%20be%20wrong%2C%20and%20Naynaba%20(Ravindra's%20sister)%20could%20be%20wrong%2C%20but%20you%20tell%20me%2C%20how%20can%20all%2050%20members%20of%20our%20family%20be%20wrong%3F%20There's%20no%20relation%20with%20anyone%20in%20the%20family%3B%20there's%20just%20hate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do