%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20informed%20through%20an%20official%20statement%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Delhi%3A%20Qatar%20released%20the%20eight%20Indian%20ex-Navy%20veterans%20who%20were%20in%20its%20custody%3B%20seven%20of%20them%20have%20returned%20to%20India.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FyuYVx5N8zR%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FyuYVx5N8zR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1756843375376916885%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20released%20an%20official%20statement%20welcoming%20the%20decision%20to%20set%20the%20veteran%20officers%20free%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Government%20of%20India%20welcomes%20the%20release%20of%20eight%20Indian%20nationals%20working%20for%20the%20Dahra%20Global%20company%20who%20were%20detained%20in%20Qatar.%20Seven%20out%20of%20the%20eight%20of%20them%20have%20returned%20to%20India.%20We%20appreciate%20the%20decision%20by%20the%20Amir%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Qatar%20to%20enable%20the%20release%20and%20home-coming%20of%20these%20nationals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eight%20Indian%20nationals%20were%20imprisoned%20in%20Qatar%20since%20October%202022%20and%20were%20accused%20of%20allegedly%20spying%20on%20a%20submarine%20programme.%20The%20retired%20naval%20personnel%20were%20sentenced%20to%20death%20by%20a%20Qatar%20court%20on%20charges%20that%20have%20not%20yet%20been%20made%20public%20officially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Qatari%20Court%20commuted%20the%20death%20penalty%20sentence%20of%20eight%20ex-Indian%20naval%20officers%20it%20had%20arrested%20last%20year%20in%20the%20Dahra%20Global%20case%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%20in%20a%20press%20statement.%20The%20sentence%20has%20now%20been%20reduced%20to%20jail%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20judgement%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20noted%20the%20verdict%20today%20of%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20of%20Qatar%20in%20the%20Dahra%20Global%20case%2C%20in%20which%20the%20sentences%20have%20been%20reduced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MEA%20also%20said%20that%20the%20detailed%20judgement%20in%20the%20case%20is%20awaited%20and%20are%20in%20close%20touch%20with%20the%20legal%20team%20in%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMEA%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20detailed%20judgement%20is%20awaited.%20We%20are%20in%20close%20touch%20with%20the%20legal%20team%20as%20well%20as%20the%20family%20members%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20next%20steps.%20Our%20Ambassador%20to%20Qatar%20and%20other%20officials%20were%20present%20in%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20today%2C%20along%20with%20the%20family%20members.%20We%20have%20stood%20by%20them%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20matter%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20extend%20all%20consular%20and%20legal%20assistance.%20We%20will%20also%20continue%20to%20take%20up%20the%20matter%20with%20the%20Qatari%20authorities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20met%20Qatar's%20Emir%20Sheikh%20Tamim%20bin%20Hamad%20Al-Thani%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20COP28%20summit%20in%20Dubai%20and%20discussed%20bilateral%20partnership%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bwell-being%20of%20the%20Indian%20community%26quot%3B%20living%20in%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20newly%20appointed%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20Jaiswal%2C%20emphasised%20the%20temporal%20significance%20of%20this%20period%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20the%20issue%20is%20concerned%2C%20there%20is%20a%20time%20of%2060%20days%20when%20this%20issue%20can%20be%20appealed%20in%20the%20Court%20of%20Cassation%2C%20which%20is%20the%20highest%20court%20in%20Qatar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MEA's%20legal%20team%20possesses%20the%20confidential%20court%20order%20detailing%20the%20commutation%20of%20the%20death%20sentences%20to%20imprisonment%20terms%2C%20a%20move%20revealed%20in%20a%20press%20release%20following%20the%20court%20of%20appeal's%20judgement%20on%20December%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20issued%20a%20press%20release%20in%20which%20we%20informed%20you%20that%20the%20death%20sentence%2C%20which%20was%20originally%20a%20death%20penalty%2C%20has%20been%20changed%20to%20imprisonment%20sentences.%20Now%20our%20legal%20team%20has%20that%20court%20order%2C%20and%20I%20can%20confirm%20that%20all%20of%20them%20have%20received%20sentences%20of%20different%20durations%2C%20and%20the%20death%20penalty%20has%20been%20abolished%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaiswal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20Court%20of%20First%20Instance%20of%20Qatar%20had%20also%20passed%20the%20judgement%20against%20them%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MEA%20spokesperson%20also%20highlighted%20the%20recent%20meeting%20that%20took%20place%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20Emir%20of%20Qatar%2C%20Sheikh%20Tamim%20Bin%20Hamad%20and%20said%20that%20they%20have%20had%20a%20good%20conversation%20on%20the%20overall%20bilateral%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707708000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Figvuh51o_indian-navy-veterans_625x300_12_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffreed-navy-veterans-chant-bharat-mata-ki-jai-praise-pm-narendra-modi-on-re