%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20statement%2C%20PPP%20leadership%20will%20put%20forward%20the%20proposals%20of%20PML-N%20in%20the%20Central%20Executive%20Committee%20meeting.%20The%20delegation%20of%20PML-N%20includes%20Azam%20Nazir%20Tarar%2C%20Ayaz%20Sadiq%2C%20Ahsan%20Iqbal%2C%20Rana%20Tanveer%2C%20Khawaja%20Saad%20Rafiq%2C%20Malik%20Ahmad%20Khan%2C%20Marriyum%20Aurangzeb%20and%20Shaza%20Fatima.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20PML-N%20President%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BLahore%3A%20President%20PPPP%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%2C%20PPP%20Chairman%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari%20met%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Muhammad%20Shahbaz%20Sharif%20at%20Bilawal%20House.%20In%20principle%20consensus%20on%20political%20cooperation%20between%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20(N)%20and%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party.%20In%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20overall%20situation%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20political%20cooperation%20in%20the%20future%20were%20discussed%20in%20detail.%20Lahore%3A%20The%20leaders%20agreed%20to%20cooperate%20politically%20to%20bring%20the%20country%20to%20political%20stability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20leaders%20of%20both%20parties%20agreed%20in%20principle%20to%20save%20the%20country%20from%20political%20instability.%20In%20the%20meeting%2C%20both%20parties%20consulted%20on%20the%20situation%20and%20discussed%20the%20proposals.%20PPP%20leadership%20will%20put%20forward%20the%20proposals%20of%20PML-N%20in%20the%20Central%20Executive%20Committee%20meeting.%20The%20majority%20of%20the%20people%20have%20given%20us%20a%20mandate%3B%20we%20will%20not%20disappoint%20the%20people%2C%20expressed%20the%20opinion%20of%20the%20leaders.%20The%20PML-N%20delegation%20includes%20Azam%20Nazir%20Tarar%2C%20Ayaz%20Sadiq%2C%20Ahsan%20Iqbal%2C%20Rana%20Tanveer%2C%20Khawaja%20Saad%20Rafiq%2C%20Malik%20Ahmad%20Khan%2C%20Marriyum%20Aurangzeb%20and%20Shaza%20Fatima%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Secretariat%20of%20the%20PPP%20Chairman%20stated%20that%20it%20was%20the%20PPP's%20first%20meeting%20with%20PML-N%20over%20the%20government's%20formation.%20The%20two%20parties%20discussed%20government%20formation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Secretariat%20of%20the%20PPP%20Chairman%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BLahore%3A%20First%20official%20contact%20of%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-N%20with%20the%20leadership%20of%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20for%20government%20formation.%20PML-N%20President%20Mian%20Shahbaz%20Sharif%20reached%20Bilawal%20House%20to%20seek%20cooperation%20from%20the%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20in%20government%20formation.%20President%20PPP%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%2C%20Chairman%20PPP%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari%20and%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Mian%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20discussed%20government%20formation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAzam%20Nazir%20Tarar%2C%20Ayaz%20Sadiq%2C%20Ahsan%20Iqbal%2C%20Rana%20Tanveer%2C%20Khawaja%20Saad%20Rafiq%2C%20Malik%20Ahmad%20Khan%2C%20Maryam%20Aurangzeb%20and%20Shaza%20Fatima%20are%20included%20in%20the%20delegation%20of%20PML-N.%20Your%20proposal%20regarding%20cooperation%20in%20government%20formation%20will%20be%20discussed%20in%20the%20Central%20Executive%20Committee%20meeting%20tomorrow%2C%20PPP%20leadership's%20reply%20to%20PML-N%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Muttahida%20Qaumi%20Movement%20-%20Pakistan%20(MQM-P)%20convener%2C%20Khalid%20Maqbool%20Siddiqui%20said%20that%20discussions%20during%20a%20meeting%20with%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20leaders%20did%20not%20involve%20any%20talks%20regarding%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20next%20government%2C%20Pakistan-based%20Dawn%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20Karachi%2C%20Siddiqui%20said%20the%20polls%20have%20created%20a%20challenging%20situation%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20stressed%20that%20all%20parties%20must%20play%20their%20part%20in%20moving%20the%20country%20out%20of%20crisis.He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20stability%20of%20democracy%20is%20more%20important%20than%20anything%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasised%20that%20no%20discussion%20has%20yet%20taken%20place%20about%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20government%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Dawn%20report.%20Khalid%20Maqbool%20Siddiqui%20said%20it%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20confirmed%20whether%20the%20MQM-P%20will%20get%20any%20share%20in%20the%20government%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20came%20shortly%20after%20the%20PML-N%20released%20a%20statement%20saying%20that%20the%20two%20parties%20had%20reached%20a%20%26quot%3Bprinciple%20agreement%26quot%3B%20to%20work%20together%20in%20the%20next%20government%2C%20according%20to%20Dawn%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20PML-N%20leader%20Marriyum%20Aurangzeb%20said%20that%20PML-N%20and%20MQM-P%20leaders%20agreed%20on%20political%20cooperation.%20She%20noted%20that%20an%20in-principle%20agreement%20was%20reached%20between%20PML-N%20supremo%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20and%20the%20MQM%20leadership.The%20delegation%20of%20PML-N%20was%20led%20by%20former%20Pakistan%20PM%20Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%20while%20MQM-P's%20delegation%20was%20led%20by%20Khalid%20Maqbool%20Siddiqui%20from%20MQM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPML-N%20leaders%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%2C%20Maryam%20Nawaz%2C%20Ishaq%20Dar%2C%20Ahsan%20Iqbal%2C%20Rana%20Sanaullah%2C%20Ayaz%20Sadiq%2C%20Khawaja%20Saad%20Rafiq%2C%20Maryam%20Aurangzeb%2C%20Rana%20Mashhood%20were%20also%20present%20in%20the%20meeting.She%20noted%20that%20the%20meeting%20between%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20continued%20for%20about%20an%20hour.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20two%20sides%20held%20a%20detailed%20consultation%20on%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Marriyum%20Aurangzeb%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BAn%20in-principle%20agreement%20was%20reached%20between%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-N%20leader%20Muhammad%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20and%20the%20MQM%20leadership%20It%20will%20go%20together%20for%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20nation%3B%20the%20basic%20points%20have%20been%20decided%20in%20Muslim%20League%20(N)%20and%20MQM.%20Muhammad%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20from%20the%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20(N)%20and%20Dr%20Khalid%20Maqbool%20Siddiqui%20from%20MQM%20led%20the%20delegation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPakistan%20Muslim%20League%20(N)%20President%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%2C%20Maryam%20Nawaz%2C%20Ishaq%20Dar%2C%20Ahsan%20Iqbal%2C%20Rana%20Sanaullah%2C%20Ayaz%20Sadiq%2C%20Khawaja%20Saad%20Rafiq%2C%20Maryam%20Aurangzeb%2C%20Rana%20Mashhood%20were%20also%20present%20in%20the%20meeting.%20The%20MQM%20delegation%20included%20Sindh%20Governor%20Kamran%20Tasuri%2C%20Dr%20Farooq%20Sattar%2C%20Mustafa%20Kamal.%20The%20consultation%20between%20the%20leaders%20of%20both%20parties%20continued%20for%20about%20an%20hour%20In%20the%20meeting%2C%20there%20was%20a%20detailed%20consultation%20on%20the%20situation%20and%20suggestions%20were%20exchanged%20The%20leaders%20also%20confided%20in%20each%20other%20regarding%20the%20overall%20political%20situation%20and%20the%20contacts%20made%20so%20far%20Earlier%2C%20on%20their%20arrival%20in%20Raiwand%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Muslim%20League%20(N)%20Muhammad%20Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%20President%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%2C%20along%20with%20the%20party%20leaders%2C%20welcomed%20the%20MQM%20leaders%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707707040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2grve2mg_bilawal-bhutto-shehbaz-sharif_625x300_12_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-general-elections-2024-bilawal-bhutto-shehbaz-sharif-agree-to-save-p