%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere's%20her%20(Nikki%20Haley's)%20husband%3F%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3B'Oh%2C%20he's%20away%2C%20he's%20away.'%20What%20happened%20to%20her%20husband%3F%20What%20happened%20to%20her%20husband%3F%20Where%20is%20he%3F%20He's%20gone%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaley's%20husband%2C%20Major%20Michael%20Haley%2C%20was%20deployed%20in%20Africa%20in%20June%20of%20last%20year%20with%20the%20South%20Carolina%20Army%20National%20Guard.%20She%20wished%20him%20farewell%20in%20a%20ceremony%20in%20mid-June%20with%20about%20200%20soldiers%20at%20The%20Citadel%2C%20a%20military%20college%20in%20Charleston.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Nikki%20Haley%20also%20attacked%20Trump%20for%20remarks%20he%20made%20about%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20is%20in%20the%20military%20and%20stationed%20abroad%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMichael%20is%20deployed%20serving%20our%20country%2C%20something%20you%20know%20nothing%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20Haley%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BSomeone%20who%20continually%20disrespects%20the%20sacrifices%20of%20military%20families%20has%20no%20business%20being%20commander%20in%20chief.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20always%20been%20my%20rock%2C%26quot%3B%20Haley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20both%20lived%20a%20life%20of%20service%2C%20and%20so%20when%20he%20goes%20off%20to%20deploy%2C%20my%20support%20is%20completely%20with%20him.%20If%20I%20happen%20to%20be%20running%20for%20president%2C%20his%20support%20is%20completely%20with%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaley%20and%20her%20husband%20have%20been%20together%20for%20more%20than%2025%20years%2C%20and%20he%20frequently%20attended%20her%20candidacy%20rallies.%20The%20former%20UN%20ambassador%20often%20discussed%20being%20married%20to%20a%20member%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%3B%20her%20husband%20joined%20the%20Natio