y-3-shahid-kapoor-and-kriti-sanon-starrer%2Farticleshow%2F107611275.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Happened%20In%20Pakistan's%20Disputed%20Election%20And%20What's%20Next%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20went%20to%20the%20polls%20last%20week%20in%20an%20election%20that%20many%20thought%20would%20be%20a%20formality.%20Former%20cricket%20star%20Imran%20Khan%20was%20in%20jail%2C%20his%20party%20banned%20from%20running%20under%20its%20own%20banner%20or%20even%20using%20its%20famous%20cricket%20bat%20symbol.%20Analysts%20said%20the%20powerful%20military%20gave%20its%20blessing%20for%20the%20three-time%20former%20premier%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20-%20or%20anyone%20else%20other%20than%20Khan%20-%20to%20take%20power%2C%20and%20Sharif's%20return%20was%20the%20most%20likely%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20surprise%20development%2C%20Khan%20loyalists%20-%20running%20as%20independents%20-%20thrived%2C%20winning%20the%20most%20seats%20of%20any%20group.%20Their%20against-the-odds%20performance%20highlighted%20voters'%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20status%20quo%20of%20Pakistan's%20politics%2C%20which%20is%20dominated%20by%20two%20family-controlled%20parties%20and%2C%20analysts%20say%2C%20the%20powerful%20military.%20It%20was%20also%20a%20triumph%20for%20democracy%2C%20leaders%20from%20Khan's%20party%20said%2C%20as%20the%20people%20of%20Pakistan%20demanded%20to%20be%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20though%20candidates%20from%20Khan's%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20party%2C%20or%20PTI%2C%20won%20the%20most%20seats%2C%20they%20may%20not%20form%20a%20government.%20That's%20because%20they%20don't%20have%20a%20simple%20majority%2C%20and%20the%20two%20other%20main%20parties%20may%20join%20forces.%20Khan%20supporters%2C%20who%20argue%20authorities%20are%20attempting%20to%20influence%20the%20outcome%2C%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20Sunday%20but%20not%20in%20large%20numbers%2C%20deterred%20by%20a%20heavy%20police%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20historic%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20party%20won%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndependents%2C%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20whom%20are%20Imran%20Khan%20loyalists%2C%20took%20101%20of%20the%20265%20contested%20lower-house%20seats.%20Sharif's%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20won%2075%2C%20while%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari's%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20got%2054.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20parties%20fell%20short%20of%20a%20simple%20majority%20of%20133%20seats.%20That%20is%20not%20surprising.%20Since%20military%20rule%20ended%20in%202006%2C%20no%20single%20party%20has%20won%20an%20outright%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sharif%20and%20Bhutto%20parties%20held%20talks%20on%20joining%20forces%2C%20a%20move%20that%20analysts%20say%20is%20likely%20backed%20by%20the%20military%2C%20but%20they%20haven't%20yet%20reached%20an%20agreement%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Khan's%20PTI%20has%20been%20complaining%20about%20the%20results%2C%20which%20it%20claims%20are%20being%20manipulated.%20It%20wants%20more%20transparency%20on%20the%20count.%20The%20US%2C%20European%20Union%20and%20UK%20have%20expressed%20similar%20concerns%2C%20while%20Pakistan's%20foreign%20ministry%20disagrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20likely%20to%20come%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20likely%20scenario%20is%20Sharif's%20party%20will%20broker%20a%20deal%20with%20Bhutto%20Zardari's%20PPP.%20Both%20parties%20could%20then%20attract%20other%20parties%20to%20the%20coalition%20and%20even%20some%20of%20the%20Khan-backed%20candidates.%20Sharif%2C%20or%20his%20brother%2C%20Shehbaz%2C%20would%20probably%20then%20become%20prime%20minister%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20not%20forget%20that%20despite%20the%20Sharif%20and%20Bhutto%20clans'%20public%20opposition%20to%20each%20other%2C%20they%20formed%20a%20government%20together%20after%20Khan's%20ouster%20in%20April%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20unlikely%2C%20but%20not%20out%20of%20the%20question%2C%20that%20Bhutto%20Zardari%2C%20the%20son%20of%20assassinated%20former%20premier%20Benazir%20Bhutto%2C%20could%20end%20up%20negotiating%20to%20lead%20any%20coalition.%20He%20has%20some%20leverage%2C%20and%20at%2035%2C%20he%20argues%20that%20he%20represents%20a%20fresh%20face%20in%20a%20country%20where%20more%20than%2060%25%20of%20the%20population%20is%20under%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20harder%20to%20see%20a%20scenario%20where%20Khan's%20PTI%20forms%20a%20government%20given%20the%20military's%20opposition%20to%20it%2C%20analysts%20say.%20But%20one%20pathway%20would%20be%20to%20form%20an%20alliance%20with%20another%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20will%20Khan's%20supporters%20respond%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20question%20is%20how%20much%20Khan's%20supporters%20will%20push%20back.%20Remember%2C%20the%20military%20already%20clamped%20down%20on%20PTI%20last%20May%20when%20supporters%20attacked%20government%20and%20military%20buildings%20after%20Khan%20was%20detained.%20Some%20observers%20say%20they're%20unlikely%20to%20have%20the%20appetite%20for%20another%20confrontation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20this%20mean%20for%20the%20military%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20outcome%20the%20military%20would%20have%20wanted.%20The%20support%20for%20Khan's%20loyalists%20is%20a%20demand%20for%20true%20democracy%20and%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20status%20quo.%20It's%20also%20clearly%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20military%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20question%20is%20what%20the%20army%20will%20do%20next.%20Pakistan's%20generals%20have%20stepped%20in%20three%20times%20in%20the%20country's%20history%20to%20directly%20rule%20the%20nuclear-armed%20nation.%20The%20last%20time%20was%20in%201999%20