20tried%20to%20embrace%20minimalism%20whenever%20the%20kids%20let%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mother%20and%20son%20wearing%20helmets%20on%20motorbike%20with%20ocean%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b9d22a7a3d271488760b8e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20riding%20a%20motorbike%20with%20her%20son.%3Cp%3EBeth%20McCarter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChoosing%20what%20to%20do%20with%20our%20car%20and%20house%20was%20another%20big%20piece%20of%20the%20puzzle.%20Now%2C%20we%20rent%20out%20our%20house%20so%20that%20we%20can%20still%20accrue%20equity%20while%20someone%20else%20pays%20the%20mortgage.%20We%20keep%20our%20car%20at%20my%20parents'%20house%20and%20also%20bunk%20with%20them%20when%20we're%20in%20town%20in%20exchange%20for%20helping%20out%20on%20the%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20our%20family%20is%20constantly%20on%20the%20move.%20We%20take%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-travel-tips-for-road-trips-international-vacations-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroad%20trips%20around%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20make%20it%20a%20point%20to%20venture%20abroad%20at%20least%20once%20a%20year.%20We%20homeschool%20and%20work%20full-time%20from%20our%20laptops%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20keep%20our%20lifestyle%20sustainable%2C%20we're%20constantly%20tweaking%20our%20budget.%20Back%20when%20we%20were%20teachers%2C%20we%20used%20to%20go%20to%20the%20mall%20and%20end%20up%20blowing%20our%20budget.%20Now%2C%20we%20know%20how%20much%20we%20enjoy%20having%20travel%20experiences%20over%20mindless%20shopping%20and%20eating%20out.%20We%20thrift%20whenever%20possible%2C%20and%20we're%20always%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20increase%20our%20income%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20found%20that%20balancing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrugal-billionaires-millionaires-lifestyle-money-car-house-habits-net-worth-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrugal%20living%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20quality%20of%20life%20is%20key%20to%20living%20out%20our%20worldschooling%20dreams%20while%20maintaining%20financial%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOur%20new%20strategy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20ability%20to%20keep%20traveling%20hinges%20on%20a%20combination%20of%20strategic%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20embrace%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Ftravel-blogger-marissa-strang-top-trends-and-favorite-destinations-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslow%20travel%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20means%20spending%20extended%20periods%20in%20each%20location%20to%20minimize%20transportation%20costs%20and%20taking%20advantage%20of%20long-stay%20discounts.%20When%20we%20were%20in%20Europe%2C%20we%20were%20surprised%20that%20renting%20a%20car%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20cost%20more%20than%20an%20entire%20month's%20lodging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20opt%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-dont-pay-for-accommodations-traveling-trusted-housesitters-review-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efree%20pet-sitting%20opportunities%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhen%20available.%20One%20time%2C%20we%20spent%20the%20Christmas%20holidays%20in%20a%20house%20next%20to%20Disney%20World%20for%20free%20in%20exchange%20for%20watching%20a%20couple%20of%20slobbery%20bulldogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20children%20looking%20out%20at%20mountains.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b9dd18ac2de4f17ee6121f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAuthor's%20children%20admiring%20mountains%20from%20a%20distance.%3Cp%3EBeth%20McCarter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20international%20travel%2C%20we%20select%20our%20next%20destination%20based%20on%20ticket%20affordability.%20While%20we%20would%20love%20to%20go%20back%20to%20Asia%20and%20Europe%2C%20our%20budget%20often%20means%20we%20have%20to%20explore%20closer%20to%20home%20for%20the%20time%20being.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20passive%20income%20stream%2C%20such%20as%20selling%20a%20digital%20product%2C%20can%20help.%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20learned%20about%20passive%20income%20earlier.%20The%20only%20downside%20is%20that%20it%20can%20take%20a%20while%20to%20develop.%20I've%20put%20several%20years%20of%20work%20into%20this%20project%2C%20but%20I%20now%20earn%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20income%20every%20month%20from%20blog%20posts%20I've%20written%20about%20both%20travel%20and%20homeschooling%20that%20include%20links%20to%20affiliate%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWorldschooling%20isn't%20a%20never-ending%20vacation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20mishaps%20along%20the%20way%20%E2%80%94%20my%20kids%20both%20caught%20COVID-19%20in%20Tahiti%20and%20I%20sprained%20my%20ankle%20in%20a%20rabbit%20hole%20in%20rural%20France.%20We've%20also%20faced%20criticism%20for%20our%20choice%20to%20travel.%20My%20in-laws%20are%20especially%20disapproving%20and%20are%20openly%20against%20homeschooling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20setback%20of%20worldschooling%20has%20been%20the%20lack%20of%20%26quot%3Badult%26quot%3B%20time.%20Finding%20personal%20space%20is%20hard%20when%20you're%20staying%20in%20hotels%20or%20small%20Airbnbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20did%20it%20for%20my%20inner%20child%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWorldschooling%2C%20for%20me%2C%20is%20also%20about%20fulfilling%20my%20childhood%20dreams.%20I%20travel%20for%20my%2011-year-old%20self%2C%20who%20spent%20countless%20hours%20dreaming%20of%20traveling%20and%20watching%20%26quot%3BHouse%20Hunters%20International.%26quot%3B%20My%20current%20lifestyle%20is%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20a%20heartfelt%20celebration%20of%20my%20inner%20child's%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20way%2C%20it's