the%20artwork%20on%20the%20walls%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20leave%20some%20of%20the%20pieces%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20it%20to%20be%20be%20more%20organic%2C%26quot%3B%20Imran%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20go%20to%20gallery%2C%20sometimes%20in%20the%20back%20room%2C%20this%20is%20how%20they%20put%20all%20the%20artwork%20too.%20They%20just%20lay%20it%20on%20the%20floor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223678%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20office.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c1a1687a3d27148877f302%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222758%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20office.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20exposed%20walls%20and%20poured%20concrete%20floor%2C%20the%20couple's%20house%20feels%20cozy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarefully%20curated%20wood%20furniture%20creates%20a%20stark%20contrast%20against%20the%20cold%20concrete%2C%20and%20the%20little%20mementos%20displayed%20all%20around%20their%20home%20give%20a%20glimpse%20into%20the%20couple's%20personalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20just%20allowed%20the%20house%20to%20be%20something%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20be%2C%20instead%20of%20planning%20too%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20Imran%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223641%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20walk-in%20closet.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c1a1677a3d27148877f2fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222731%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20walk-in%20closet.%20The%20door%20on%20the%20left%20leads%20to%20the%20couple's%20bedroom%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EGetting%20the%20'construction%20site'%20vision%20across%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Imran%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20was%20getting%20Fadzeera%20to%20understand%20his%20design%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20time%2C%20I%20asked%20her%20if%20she%20ever%20envisioned%20her%20house%20looking%20like%20a%20construction%20site%2C%26quot%3B%20Imran%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20wanted%20to%20use%20materials%20like%20stainless%20steel%20for%20the%20kitchen%2C%20but%20she%20was%20unsure%20how%20the%20final%20outcome%20would%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223799%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20master%20bedroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c1a1686fcb546d2d4c6efa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222848%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20master%20bedroom.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20fear%20is%20having%20materials%20like%20stainless%20steel%2C%20right%3F%20It's%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20is%20it%20going%20to%20look%20like%20an%20abattoir%3F'%20or%20'It's%20going%20to%20look%20cold%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20had%20to%20assure%20me%20that%20everything%20will%20look%20ok%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20it%20worked%20out%20like%20Imran%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20now%20I%20cannot%20imagine%20a%20life%20without%20a%20stainless%20steel%20kitchen%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20so%20easy%20to%20clean%2C%26quot%3B%20Fadzeera%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELetting%20their%20personality%20shine%20through%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223827%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20room%20and%20balcony%20area.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c2e6157a3d271488786451%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222870%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20room%20and%20balcony%20area.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EImran's%20favorite%20part%20of%20the%20home%20is%20the%20office%2C%20while%20Fadzeera%20loves%20the%20dining%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20have%20my%20friends%20o