%20of%20having%20children%20far%20exceed%20the%20upsides.%20By%20not%20having%20kids%2C%20I%20only%20need%20to%20worry%20about%20my%20retirement%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20person%20wrote%20on%20the%20microblogging%20platform%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F6633074403%2FNuGdqB734%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWeibo%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20cited%20the%20loss%20of%20personal%20freedom%20as%20a%20key%20obstacle%20to%20having%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20having%20kids%20means%20I%20can%20spend%20all%20my%20money%20on%20myself.%20I%20can%20take%20an%20overseas%20vacation%20whenever%20I%20like%2C%20sleep%20in%20on%20the%20weekends%2C%20and%20go%20out%20drinking%20late%20at%20night.%20That%20beats%20worrying%20about%20my%20kids%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20person%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F6633074403%2FNuGdqB734%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFrom%20baby%20boom%20to%20bust%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20looming%20demographic%20crisis%20has%20been%20a%20source%20of%20worry%20for%20China's%20leaders.%20At%20last%20year's%20National%20Women's%20Congress%2C%20China's%20leader%2C%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20said%20China%20needs%20to%20%26quot%3Bactively%20cultivate%20a%20new%20culture%20of%20marriage%20and%20childbearing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20strengthen%20our%20guidance%20on%20marriage%2C%20childbirth%2C%20and%20family%20planning%20for%20our%20youths.%20We%20need%20to%20promote%20and%20implement%20pro-fertility%20policies%20and%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20our%20human%20capital%20while%20taking%20care%20of%20our%20aging%20population%2C%26quot%3B%20Xi%20said%20in%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Fyaowen%2Fliebiao%2F202310%2Fcontent_6912723.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espeech%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20setting%20up%20a%20ba