ring%20the%20digital%20ecosystem%20that%20disseminates%20divisive%20narratives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journalists%20highlighted%20how%20individuals%20appeared%20in%20various%20roles%20across%20videos%20to%20promote%20specific%20political%20agendas%2C%20illustrating%20a%20symbiotic%20relationship%20between%20YouTubers%20and%20political%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20lot%20of%20cases%2C%20the%20same%20individual%20appeared%20in%20different%20roles%20in%20videos%20pushing%20a%20particular%20political%20narrative.%20It%20is%20a%20symbiotic%20relationship%20wherein%20the%20YouTubers%20are%20earning%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20and%20the%20political%20parties%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20propaganda%20content%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20two%20winners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Week%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Findia%2F2024%2F02%2F09%2Ffreelance-journalists-neel-madhav-alishan-jafri-win-ipi-india-award-for-excellence-in-journalism.html%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Justice%20Lokur%2C%20who%20presided%20over%20the%20function%2C%20as%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9COver%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20we%20have%20had%20an%20overdose%20of%20hate.%20In%20most%20instances%2C%20it%20was%20restricted%20to%20hate%20speech%2C%20but%20soon%20the%20venom%20became%20more%20poisonous%20and%20resulted%20in%20violence%20against%20innocent%20persons%2C%20including%20youngsters.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20restrictive%20or%20coercive%20action%20by%20the%20police%2C%20vigilante%20groups%20got%20emboldened%20and%20the%20consequence%20was%20an%20outbreak%20of%20lynching.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20an%20unintended%20consequence%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20giving%20directions%20on%20the%20matter%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20data%20about%20lynching%20vanished%20from%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20and%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20stopped%20collecting%20data%20on%20lynching.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEminent%20jurist%20F.S.%20Nariman%2C%20while%20presenting%20the%20award%2C%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20decline%20of%20press%20freedom%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20past%20the%20age%20of%20free%20speech%20and%20entering%20another%20age%20%E2%80%93%20an%20age%20of%20thought%20control.%20You%20will%20say%20what%20thought-control%20prompts%20you%20to%20say.%20It%20is%20a%20serious%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20after%20watching%20a%20video%20made%20by%20the%20two%20award-winning%20scribes%20on%20how%20they%20exposed%20rackets%20that%20were%20making%20fake%20videos%20and%20spreading%20hate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20drop%20in%20the%20world%20press%20freedom%20index%20is%20that%20governments%20at%20the%20Centre%20or%20state%20operate%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20much%20of%20the%20media%20are%20compelled%20to%20look%20over%20their%20shoulder%20to%20see%20if%20government%20officials%20are%20smiling%20at%20them.%20The%20condition%20is%20not%20at%20all%20suited%20for%20a%20free%20press%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nariman.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707653118000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11171229%2Fimage-1823.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fneel-madhav-and-alishan-jafri-win-ipi-india-award-for-excellence-in-journalism-in-the-caravan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Their%20story%2C%20titled%20'Clicks%20and%20Bait'%2C%20exposed%20how%20a%20group%20of%20YouTubers%20were%20setting%20the%20agenda%20for%20television%20debates%20and%20creating%20bulk%20content%20for%20certain%20political%20parties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fneel-madhav-and-alishan-jafri-win-ipi-india-award-for-excellence-in-journalism-in-the-caravan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arambai%E2%80%99s%20Political%20Sway%20Is%20Not%20Only%20in%20Imphal%20but%20Far%20Beyond%20It.%20Yet%20the%20State%20Turns%20a%20Blind%20Eye%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04223216%2Fimage-968.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20an%20exclusive%20event%20at%20the%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%20(ORF)%20on%20February%205%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgovernment-ended-border-racial-and-religious-disputes-in-ne-in-the-past-nine-years-amit-shah%2Farticle67815434.ece%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20ruling%20government%20had%20ended%20%E2%80%9Cborder%2C%20ethnic%20and%20religious%20disputes%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Northeast.%20The%20timing%20of%20his%20claim%20is%20jarring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20fortnight%20earlier%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20Manipur%2C%20which%20has%20been%20embroiled%20in%20an%20intense%20ethnic%20conflict%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki-Zomi%20communities%20since%20May%2C%20witnessed%20what%20can%20only%20be%20called%20a%20hostile%20takeover%20of%20the%20state%20machinery%20by%20a%20militia.%20On%20January%2024%2C%20Arambai%20Tenggol%2C%20a%20Meitei%20ethnic%20militia%2C%20accused%20of%20attacks%20against%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Kuki-Zomi%20population%2C%20summoned%2039%20Meitei%20lawmakers%20in%20Imphal%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fmanipur-group-sets-peace-terms-for-cm-mlas%2Farticle67772535.ece%5C%22%3Eadministered%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmeitei-radical-group-extracts-pledge-from-legislators-for-peace-in-manipur-within-15-days%5C%22%3Ean%20%E2%80%9Coath%E2%80%9D%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20among%20others%2C%20protect%20%E2%80%9CManipur%E2%80%99s%20territorial%20integrity%E2%80%9D.%20They%20were%20made%20to%20sign%20a%20six-point%20charter%20of%20demands%2C%20which%20was%20then%20sent%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20with%20an%20implementation%20deadline%20of%2015%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Cceremony%E2%80%9D%20was%20held%20at%20the%20iconic%20Kangla%20Fort%2C%20the%20traditional%20seat%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Meitei%20kingdom.%20According%20to%20media%20reports%2C%20the%20Arambai%20cadres%20not%20only%20forced%20the%20state%20police%20to%20keep%20out%2C%20but%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fmlas-summoned-by-arambai-tenggol-were-beaten-up-when-they-didnt-agree-to-demands-legislator-says%2F1938631%2F%5C%22%3Eroughed%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20some%20of%20the%20lawmakers%20present.%20Among%20those%20reportedly%20beaten%20up%20were%20two%20Members%20of%20Legislative%20Assembly%20(MLAs)%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20which%20rules%20the%20state.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1062725%2Fin-imphal-the-states-surrender-to-an-armed-meitei-militia-with-taliban-like-grip%5C%22%3EPaonam%20Brojen%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Meitei%20Christian%2C%20who%20is%20seen%20to%20be%20a%20political%20opponent%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20whose%20Imphal%20property%20was%20vandalised%20by%20an%20Arambai-led%20mob%20in%20early%20May.%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20chief%2C%20K.%20Meghachandra%2C%20was%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fcongress-manipur-chief-assault-meitei-outfit-centre-9129661%2F%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20assaulted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20the%20whole%20ceremony%2C%20conducted%20under%20duress%2C%20was%20nothing%20short%20of%20an%20insurrection%20%E2%80%93%20a%20direct%20challenge%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20authority%20to%20enforce%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20parallel%20state%20emerges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFew%20in%20the%20national%20commentariat%20have%20understood%20the%20real%20gravity%20or%20political%20and%20constitutional%20ramifications%20of%20what%20happened%20in%20Imphal%20on%20January%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20multi-layered%20security%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ebandobast%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20with%20personnel%20drawn%20from%20the%20nearly%2060%2C000%20central%20and%20state%20security%20forces%20operating%20under%20the%20Unified%20Command%20in%20Manipur%2C%20including%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF)%2C%20were%20to%20be%20stationed%20outside%20all%20the%20entrances%20to%20the%20fort%20to%20stop%20the%20Arambai%20cadres%20from%20entering.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fmlas-summoned-by-arambai-tenggol-were-beaten-up-when-they-didnt-agree-to-demands-legislator-says%2F1938631%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20security%20cover%20was%20withdrawn%20at%20the%20last%20moment.%20No%20one%20knows%20who%20gave%20the%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1062725%2Fin-imphal-the-states-surrender-to-an-armed-meitei-militia-with-taliban-like-grip%5C%22%3EPhotos%3C%2Fa%3E%20captured%20by%20%3Cem%3EScroll%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20Arunabh%20Saikia%20show%20Arambai%20cadres%20in%20camouflage%20manning%20the%20fort%E2%80%99s%20main%20gate%2C%20along%20with%20open-top%20Gypsy%20cars%2C%20adorned%20with%20the%20Salai%20Taret%20flag%2C%20which%20once%20represented%20the%20seven%20Meitei%20clans%20of%20the%20Meitei%20kingdom%2C%20parked%20outside%20the%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20pictures%2C%20an%20uninitiated%20observer%20might%20think%20the%20Arambai%20was%20an%20official%20paramilitary%20force.%20They%20would%20probably%20not%20know%20that%20its%20members%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1059169%2Fmanipur-family-of-abducted-kuki-zos-file-fir-against-arambai-tenggol-other-outfits%5C%22%3Emurder%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3Erape%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fprotection-money-to-arambai-tenggol-how-traders-are-operating-in-strife-torn-imphal%2F1938796%2F%5C%22%3Eextortion%20and%20collection%20of%20%E2%80%98protection%20money%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20forcing%20Meitei%20Christians%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewlinesmag.com%2Freportage%2Fmeitei-christians-in-indias-manipur-face-broad-attacks%2F%5C%22%3Edenounce%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20religion%20at%20gun%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20didn%E2%80%99t%20end%20at%20Kangla%20Fort.%20It%20spilled%20out%20onto%20the%20streets%20of%20Imphal.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCD67VCc-D6A%5C%22%3EVideos%20circulating%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20social%20media%20show%20the%20Arambai%E2%80%99s%20influential%20%E2%80%9CCommander-in-Chief%E2%80%9D%2C%20Korunungba%20Khuman%2C%20dressed%20in%20pastel%20green%20camouflage%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnXBvb9Pacbg%3Fsi%3DKmPryQ9nFvcNfe-E%5C%22%3Egetting%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20vehicle%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9CPolice%E2%80%9D%20sticker%20pasted%20on%20its%20windshield%20and%20proudly%20marching%20to%20the%20famous%20%E2%80%9CIma%20Keithel%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9CMother%E2%80%99s%20Market%E2%80%9D%20along%20with%20his%20lieutenants%2C%20as%20a%20rapturous%20crowd%20raising%20the%20Salai%20Taret%20flag%20cheered%20them%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stage-managed%20histrionics%20of%20it%20all%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20underestimated.%20The%20%E2%80%9Coath%E2%80%9D%20ceremony%20and%20Arambai%E2%80%99s%20triumphant%20parade%20afterwards%20marked%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20new%20social%20contract%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20one%20that%20allows%20an%20extrajudicial%20entity%20to%20claim%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20legitimacy%20and%20monopoly%20over%20violence.%20Even%20%E2%80%9CHobbessian%20anarchy%E2%80%9D%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20fully%20describe%20this%20dissolution%20of%20state%20power%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Arambai%20administered%20the%20oath%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Sanamahi%2C%20a%20Meitei%20deity%2C%20lending%20the%20whole%20event%20a%20ethno-religious%20flavour.%20The%20demands%20included%20the%20removal%20of%20%E2%80%9CKuki%20illegal%20immigrants%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20list%20and%20conducting%20an%20Assam-like%20exercise%20to%20create%20a%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20for%20Manipur%20with%201951%20as%20the%20base%20year.%20Both%20flow%20from%20the%20mischaracterisation%20by%20the%20Metei%20political%20elite%20and%20civil%20society%20of%20the%20Hills-based%20tribal%20community%20as%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrants%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cinterlopers%E2%80%9D%20from%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20Behind%20the%20Manipur%20Violence%20and%20Why%20Stopping%20It%20Poses%20a%20Test%20for%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20challenge%20to%20state%20authority%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20summoning%20elected%20constitutional%20functionaries%20and%20forcing%20them%20to%20abandon%20their%20sworn%20oath%20of%20office%20to%20uphold%20the%20Indian%20constitution%2C%20while%20coercing%20them%20to%20take%20an%20ethno-political%20pledge%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20affront%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20national%20security%20and%20political%20integrity%2C%20then%20what%20is%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%2C%20what%20is%20even%20more%20striking%20is%20that%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20is%20directly%20and%20morally%20implicated%20in%20this%20extra-constitutional%20event%20as%20a%20Union%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20Rajkumar%20Ranjan%20Singh%2C%20the%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20External%20Affairs%20%E2%80%93%20was%20also%20amongst%20the%20functionaries%20who%20took%20the%20oath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20by%20the%20logic%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20anti-terror%20law%2C%20Arambai%E2%80%99s%20actions%20from%20May%203%20onwards%20(and%2C%20specifically%20the%20January%2024%20event)%20amount%20to%20%E2%80%9Cterrorist%20act(s)%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20threat%20to%20national%20security.%20Their%20actions%20fall%20squarely%20within%20the%20four%20corners%20of%20what%20is%20punishable%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA)%2C%201967.%20They%20were%20undertaken%2C%20among%20others%2C%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cintent%20to%20strike%20terror%20in%20the%20people%E2%80%9D%20and%20to%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6compel%20the%20State%20Government%20or%20the%20Government%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%20to%20fulfil%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Arambai%20is%20yet%20to%20face%20the%20music%20from%20the%20state.%20Let%20alone%20legal%20action%2C%20the%20Manipur%20police%20has%20not%20detained%20a%20single%20member%20of%20the%20armed%20group%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Coath-taking%E2%80%9D%20ceremony%20and%20the%20alleged%20violence%20against%20elected%20lawmakers.%20Neither%20has%20the%20state%20government%2C%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20chief%20minister%2C%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20condemned%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-a-land-of-settled-grief%5C%22%3EManipur%3A%20A%20Land%20of%20Settled%20Grief%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Robinhood%20militia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20Imphal%20and%20New%20Delhi%20have%20watched%20from%20the%20wings%20as%20Arambai%2C%20which%20had%20relatively%20lesser%20influence%20in%20Manipur%20before%20May%2C%20steadily%20grew%20in%20scope%20and%20size%20while%20chipping%20away%20at%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20authority%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fimphal-heavy-firing-manipur-rifles-and-armed-mob%5C%22%3Elooting%20arms%20from%20police%20armouries%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fmanipur%2Fstory%2Fgunfight-erupts-between-arambai-tenggol-militants-and-37-assam-rifles-in-manipur-567375-2023-05-30%5C%22%3Eattacking%20central%20forces%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJamangKuki%2Fstatus%2F1721167803989025180%2Fvideo%2F1%5C%22%3Ebrandishing%20weapons%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20public%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20militias%20is%20a%20complex%20phenomenon%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20context%20of%20an%20active%20multi-ethnic%20conflict.%20So%2C%20there%20may%20be%20many%20reasons%20why%20the%20Arambai%20managed%20to%20break%20through%20the%20glass%20wall%20of%20public%20opinion%20and%20become%20somewhat%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9CRobinhood%20militia%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20a%20clear%20factor%20behind%20its%20ascendance%20is%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20critical%20political%20vacuum%20in%20Meitei%20society%20since%20the%20conflict%20began%20in%20May.%20It%20is%20likely%20that%20large%20sections%20of%20the%20population%20no%20longer%20trust%20the%20Singh%20government%20to%20protect%20their%20interests.%20Arambai%20emerged%20as%20a%20more%20viable%20and%20compelling%20alternative%2C%20not%20least%20because%20of%20its%20resolute%20military%20action%20at%20the%20frontlines.%20Despite%20growing%20evidence%20of%20their%20role%20in%20perpetuating%20violence%20against%20the%20Kuki-Zomis%2C%20an%20editor%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EPeople%E2%80%99s%20Chronicle%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20Imphal-based%20publication%2C%20had%20called%20the%20militia%E2%80%99s%20role%20and%20influence%20in%20Manipur%20since%20May%20as%20being%20akin%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F06%2F09%2Fa-pen-can-do-more-harm-than-a-gun-in-manipur-meitei-owned-media-is-winning-the-perception-war%5C%22%3EWhatsApp%20group%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meitei%20public%20now%20sees%20the%20Arambai%20as%20a%20unifying%20political%20force%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20their%20rightful%20military%20representative.%20For%20them%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Coath-taking%E2%80%9D%20ceremony%20was%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20discipline%20Meitei%20lawmakers%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum%20and%20compel%20them%20to%20uphold%20core%20concerns%20of%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20Kangla%20Fort%20event%2C%20with%20all%20its%20spectacular%20symbolism%20and%20political%20iconography%2C%20has%20thickened%20the%20air%20of%20myth%20and%20enigma%20around%20Arambai%20Tenggol%2C%20a%20name%20that%20evocatively%20refers%20to%20the%20dart-wielding%20calvary%20force%20of%20the%20ancient%20Meitei%20kingdom%20of%20Kangleipak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBroad%20appeal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20Arambai%20seems%20to%20have%20become%20even%20more%20popular%20than%20the%20established%20(and%20proscribed)%20Meitei%20armed%20groups%2C%20such%20as%20the%20United%20National%20Liberation%20Front%20(UNLF)%2C%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%2C%20and%20Kanglei%20Yawol%20Kanna%20Lup%20(KYKL).%20It%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20more%20successful%20than%20these%20older%20insurgent%20groups%20in%20drawing%20the%20disenchanted%20and%20disgruntled%20Meitei%20youth%20into%20a%20programme%20of%20patriotism%20and%20direct%20action.%20In%20fact%2C%20even%20in%20terms%20of%20actual%20armed%20action%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20the%20Arambai%20appear%20to%20have%20overshadowed%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20older%20groups%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20potential%20turf%20war%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%20worrying%20perhaps%20is%20that%20the%20Arambai%E2%80%99s%20soaring%20influence%20among%20the%20Meiteis%2C%20including%20their%20public%20figures%2C%20will%20further%20discourage%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20from%20acting%20against%20it.%20By%20moving%20against%20the%20group%2C%20Biren%20Singh%20could%20alienate%20his%20core%20constituencies%20and%20thus%2C%20make%20himself%20less%20politically%20valuable%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20high%20command.%20This%20creates%20a%20fatal%20deadlock%2C%20which%20allows%20the%20Arambai%20to%20not%20just%20persist%2C%20but%20also%20grow%20even%20bigger%20and%20stronger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20prominent%20Meitei%20personalities%2C%20such%20as%20Bollywood%20actress%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC2h1D58tWMo%2F%3Figsh%3DMXR3d3AxMWRyeXp1eg%3D%3D%5C%22%3ELin%20Laishram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Licypriya%20Kangujam%2C%20a%2012-year-old%20climate%20activist%2C%20have%20publicly%20expressed%20their%20support%20for%20the%20Arambai%20on%20social%20media.%20Licypriya%20had%20even%20mobilised%20funds%20for%20the%20purchase%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthefrontiermanipur.com%2Fchild-activist-licypriya-hands-over-thermal-drones-items-to-at%2F%5C%22%3Ethermal%20imaging%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20militia%20to%20use%20in%20their%20fight%20against%20what%20she%20called%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20Kuki%20Narco%20Terrorist%E2%80%9D.%20Using%20social%20service%20acts%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fksherson.thoudam%2Fposts%2Fpfbid02dx7VHC69FmiAkXpsWxuUeYz8uFihf6yqME9fij8mzq8qaVkqYDThaSqyneCBhZfMl%5C%22%3Edistributing%20aid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Meitei%20relief%20camps%2C%20the%20Arambai%20has%20been%20able%20to%20command%20wide%20appeal%20in%20Meitei%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECollusion%20with%20state%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarious%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-more-than-five-dead-dozens-injured-over-the-last-two-weeks-amid-ongoing-ethnic-unrest%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20mainstream%20and%20social%20media%20have%20indicated%20that%20the%20Arambai%20enjoys%20high-profile%20patronage%20from%20the%20Meitei%20ruling%20elite.%20Even%20before%20the%20conflict%20began%20in%20May%2C%20it%20had%20the%20attention%20of%20senior%20political%20figures.%20Pictures%20from%20August%202022%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Farambai-tenggol-group-manipur-meitei-mla-9128683%2F%5C%22%3Eshow%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20militia%E2%80%99s%20leader%2C%20Khuman%2C%20sitting%20with%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20Leishemba%20Sanajaoba%2C%20the%20titular%20king%20of%20Manipur%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP.%20A%20Facebook%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHHSanajaoba.Leishemba%2Fvideos%2Foath-taking-ceremony-of-arambai-tenggol-group-at-my-residence250922%2F430995689136627%2F%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20September%20that%20year%20shows%20cadres%20taking%20some%20kind%20of%20oath%20at%20Sanajaoba%E2%80%99s%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zomi%20community%20have%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1050361%2Farmed-gangs-and-a-partisan-state-how-manipur-slipped-into-civil-war%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20state%20police%20of%20providing%20cover%20to%20Arambai%20cadres%20during%20violent%20attacks%20against%20their%20villages.%20Kuki-Zomi%20organisations%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fmanipur%2Fsecurity-forces-struggle-to-recover-snatched-weapons-in-conflict-hit-manipur-2656856%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20police%20of%20handing%20over%20arms%20to%20Arambai%20members%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20have%20openly%20flaunted%20them%20in%20public.%20This%20marks%20a%20sinister%20blurring%20of%20lines%20between%20state%20and%20non-state%20armed%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20why%20has%20this%20happened%3F%20One%20reason%20could%20be%20that%20the%20Manipur%20government%20was%20keen%20on%20delegating%20the%20mandate%20of%20law%20enforcement%20to%20other%20actors.%20But%2C%20there%20may%20be%20other%20factors%20in%20an%20ethnically%20loaded%20context.%20Writing%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F24546330%3Fseq%3D1%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJournal%20of%20Conflict%20Resolution%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sabine%20C.%20Carey%2C%20Michael%20P.%20Colaresi%20and%20Neil%20J.%20Mitchell%20argue%20that%20%E2%80%9Cgovernments%20perceive%20ties%20to%20militias%20as%20a%20mechanism%20to%20evade%20accountability%20and%20muddy%20the%20flow%20of%20information%20about%20who%20is%20responsible%20for%20violence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20reminded%20of%20the%20Arab%20Janjaweed%20militia%20in%20Sudan%2C%20which%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20government%2C%20wreaked%20havoc%20in%20the%20Darfur%20region%20two%20decades%20ago.%20It%20showed%20the%20world%20the%20catastrophic%20consequences%20of%20a%20government%20giving%20%3Cem%3Ecarte%20blanche%3C%2Fem%3E%20(and%20access%20to%20small%20arms)%20to%20an%20ethnic%20militia.%20The%20example%20of%20Libya%20after%202011%20also%20comes%20to%20mind.%20The%20vacuum%20that%20the%20killing%20of%20Muammar%20al-Qaddafi%20by%20NATO-linked%20forces%20left%20was%20quickly%20filled%20up%20by%20various%20militias%2C%20which%20then%20went%20on%20to%20claim%20state%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20one%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20go%20that%20far.%20Right%20next%20to%20Manipur%2C%20the%20Myanmar%20military%20has%20been%20using%20a%20violent%20militia%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprogressivevoicemyanmar.org%2F2022%2F03%2F12%2Fthe-rising-of-pyu-saw-htee%2F%5C%22%3EPyu%20Saw%20Htee%20(PSH)%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fight%20its%20dirty%20war%20against%20pro-democracy%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-violence-claims-counterclaims-meitei-kuki%5C%22%3EDispelling%20Some%20Misleading%20Claims%20About%20the%20Violence%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArambai%E2%80%99s%20growing%20political%20shadow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20demands%20that%20Arambai%20had%20made%20in%20its%20%E2%80%9Cresolution%E2%80%9D%20during%20the%20Kangla%20event%20was%20fencing%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border.%20It%20had%20given%20New%20Delhi%2015%20days%20to%20fulfil%20the%20demand.%20On%20February%203%2C%20Singh%20travelled%20to%20New%20Delhi%20to%20meet%20Shah%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNBirenSingh%2Fstatus%2F1753733494499332544%5C%22%3Erevealed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20government%20was%20%E2%80%9Cset%20to%20take%20some%20important%20decisions%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20later%2C%20and%2012%20days%20after%20Arambai%20made%20its%20demands%2C%20Shah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-to-fence-indo-myanmar-border-says-amit-shah-work-underway-in-arunachal-pradesh-and-manipur-11707231157754.html%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20would%20fence%20the%20entire%20border.%20Two%20days%20later%2C%20he%20announced%20that%20the%20home%20ministry%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmitShah%2Fstatus%2F1755482704152305786%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1755482704152305786%257Ctwgr%255E597147d62001f291c1d58d0a8285008a89cbd22c%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Findianexpress.com%252Farticle%252Findia%252Ffree-movement-regime-india-myanmar-amit-shah-9150557%252F%5C%22%3Esuspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Free%20Movement%20Regime%20(FMR)%20that%20allows%20visa-free%20travel%20along%20the%2016-kilometre%20band%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20wonders%20if%20these%20big-ticket%20decisions%20are%20directly%20linked%20to%20Arambai%E2%80%99s%20demands%20(and%20deadline).%20If%20so%2C%20it%20is%20a%20deeply%20worrying%20sign%20of%20New%20Delhi%20giving%20in%20to%20an%20anarchic%20power%20in%20Manipur.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20sign%20of%20Arambai%E2%80%99s%20political%20sway%20in%20not%20just%20Imphal%2C%20but%20far%20beyond%20it%2C%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20two%20days%20before%20the%20Kangla%20event%2C%20an%20official%20central%20delegation%20composed%20of%20the%20interlocutor%20for%20the%20Kuki-Zomi%20insurgent%20groups%2C%20%5Borganised%20under%20the%20United%20People%E2%80%99s%20Front%20(UPF)%20and%20the%20Kuki%20National%20Organization%20(KNO)%5D%2C%20A.K.%20Mishra%2C%20and%20two%20senior%20officials%20from%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20(IB)%20were%20rushed%20to%20Imphal%20to%20hold%20a%20series%20of%20meetings%20with%20the%20Arambai.%20It%20is%20likely%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20reach%20a%20compromise%20to%20prevent%20a%20coup%20d%E2%80%99etat%20in%20Manipur.%20Clearly%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20too%2C%20can%E2%80%99t%20dismiss%2C%20let%20alone%20challenge%2C%20the%20militia%E2%80%99s%20influence%20in%20Imphal.%20In%20turn%2C%20Arambai%20is%20able%20to%20cement%20its%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerely%20two%20days%20after%20the%20Kangla%20Fort%20event%2C%20the%20state%20government%20hosted%20Republic%20Day%20at%20the%20same%20location.%20In%20his%20speech%2C%20Singh%20paid%20homage%20to%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20and%20urged%20the%20people%20to%20%E2%80%9Crespect%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20and%20one%20another%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D.%E2%80%9D%20The%20absurd%20irony%20isn%E2%80%99t%20lost%20on%20anyone%2C%20one%20hopes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20the%20political%20forces%20behind%20its%20meteoric%20rise%20are%20ultimately%20prosecuted%20or%20not%20is%20a%20different%20matter.%20The%20fact%20remains%20that%20on%20January%2024%2C%20the%20death%20knell%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20rang%20loud%20with%20a%20deafening%20shrillness%20from%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20Kangla%20Fort.%20The%20Modi%20government%20now%20has%20three%20choices%20%E2%80%93%20to%20shut%20the%20din%2C%20to%20shut%20its%20own%20ears%2C%20or%20to%20jive%20along%20with%20it.%20It%20is%20entirely%20up%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20home%20minister%20to%20take%20their%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJohn%20Simte%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Eis%20an%20advocate%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EAngshuman%20Choudhury%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Eis%20an%20Associate%20Fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Research%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707652842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04223216%2Fimage-968.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-arambai-tenggol-imphal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Whether%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20the%20political%20forces%20behind%20its%20meteoric%20rise%20are%20ultimately%20prosecuted%20or%20not%20is%20a%20different%20matter.%20The%20fact%20remains%20that%20on%20January%2024%2C%20the%20death%20knell%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20rang%20loud%20with%20a%20deafening%20shrillness%20from%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20Kangla%20Fort.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-arambai-tenggol-imphal%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inox%20Wind%20eyes%20profit%20in%20coming%20quarters%20amid%20market%20upswing%3A%20INOXGFL%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707651403000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2017-05%2F15%2Ffull%2F1494872066-6986.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Finox-wind-eyes-profit-in-coming-quarters-amid-market-upswing-inoxgfl-124021100351_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Friday%2C%20Inox%20Wind%20posted%20a%20consolidated%20net%20profit%20of%20Rs%201.81%20crore%20for%20the%20October-December%202023%20period%20after%20reporting%20a%20back-to-back%20loss%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Finox-wind-eyes-profit-in-coming-quarters-amid-market-upswing-inoxgfl-124021100351_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Finox-wind-eyes-profit-in-coming-quarters-amid-market-upswing-inoxgfl-124021100351_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Finox-wind-eyes-profit-in-coming-quarters-amid-market-upswing-inoxgfl-124021100351_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Changing%20Place%20Names%20May%20Soon%20Be%20Punishable%20in%20Manipur%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18103704%2FF6AFcQWaIAIi2H2.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Using%20place%20names%20not%20authorised%20by%20the%20government%20may%20soon%20be%20a%20punishable%20offence%20in%20Manipur.%20A%20Bill%20that%20proposes%20this%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20tabled%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Manipur%20assembly%20session%2C%20as%20per%20a%20news%20report%20by%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fstrife-torn-manipur-new-law-changing-names-places-punishable-9155003%2F%5C%22%3E%20the%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%209%2C%20the%20Manipur%20government%20announced%20that%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20next%20assembly%20session%20will%20begin%20on%20February%2028.%20One%20of%20the%20Bills%20that%20the%20government%20might%20table%20during%20the%20session%20is%20titled%20the%20%E2%80%98Manipur%20Names%20of%20Places%20Bill%2C%202024%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20for%20the%20Bill%20has%20been%20prepared%20by%20the%20Land%20Resources%20Department%20and%20approved%20by%20the%20state%20cabinet%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20news%20report%2C%20dated%20February%2011%2C%20said.%20Per%20the%20report%2C%20the%20objective%20is%20to%20establish%20%E2%80%9Can%20institutional%20mechanism%20to%20enforce%20correct%20use%20of%20names%20of%20places%E2%80%9D%20as%20well%20as%20to%20%E2%80%9Clay%20down%20procedures%20for%20giving%20names%20to%20places%2C%20and%20also%20for%20altering%20names%20of%20places%E2%80%9D.%20Per%20the%20Bill%2C%20offenders%20will%20be%20punished%20with%20a%20penalty%2C%20and%20can%20receive%20one%20to%20three%20years%20of%20imprisonment%20upon%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20new%20Bill%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98Place%20Names%20Committee%E2%80%99%20will%20be%20created%20to%20make%20recommendations%20on%20the%20names%2C%20subject%20to%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20government.%20The%20latest%20news%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20proposal%20for%20the%20Act%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20multiple%20instances%20of%20the%20use%20of%20unauthorised%20names%20of%20places%20by%20certain%20individuals%20or%20groups%20of%20people%20or%20organisations%2C%20with%20possible%20malafide%20intent%2C%20which%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20create%20confusion%20in%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20state.%E2%80%9D%20The%20proposal%20also%20lists%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccertain%20administrative%20challenges%20are%20also%20faced%20due%20to%20such%20unauthorised%20use%20of%20names%20of%20places%20at%20the%20time%20of%20discharging%20their%20duties%20by%20government%20officials%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENames%20of%20places%20have%20been%20a%20contested%20issue%20since%20violence%20began%20in%20Manipur%20in%20May%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20prominent%20example%E2%80%9D%20is%20that%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zomi-dominated%20district%20Churachandpur%20and%20its%20district%20headquarters%2C%20also%20called%20Churachandpur.%20The%20district%20and%20town%20is%20named%20after%20a%20Meitei%20king%20of%20the%20former%20Manipur%20kingdom%2C%20Churachand%20Singh%2C%20who%20ruled%20the%20area%20from%201891%20to%201941.%20But%20people%20from%20the%20Kuki-Zomi%20community%20have%20been%20calling%20the%20town%20%E2%80%9CLamka%E2%80%9D%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Both%20the%20names%20are%20over%20a%20hundred%20years%20old%2C%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20after%20the%20violence%20erupted%2C%20the%20name%20Lamka%20began%20appearing%20on%20homes%2C%20shops%20and%20even%20government%20institutions%20and%20offices.%20Similarly%2C%20resident%20Meiteis%20now%20call%20Paite%20Veng%20(Paite%20is%20a%20Zo%20sub-tribe%20and%20Veng%20means%20colony)%20in%20Imphal%20%E2%80%98Kwakeithel%20Ningthemkol%E2%80%99%20via%20a%20signboard%2C%20the%20news%20report%20highlighted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Manipur%20government%2C%20via%20an%20order%20by%20the%20chief%20secretary%2C%20told%20organisations%20and%20individuals%20to%20not%20change%20names%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdistricts%2C%20sub-divisions%2C%20places%2C%20institutions%2C%20and%20addresses%20of%20such%20institutions%E2%80%9D%20on%20their%20own%20%E2%80%93%20which%20could%20create%20possible%20conflict%20between%20communities%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fdont-change-names-of-places-warns-manipur-government%2Farticle67393496.ece%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20assembly%20session%20will%20be%20only%20the%20second%20so%20far%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20on%20May%203%20last%20year.%20As%20per%20latest%20official%20figures%20%E2%80%93%20as%20of%20September%2015%20last%20year%20%E2%80%93%20the%20violence%20has%20killed%20175%20people%20and%20injured%201%2C118%3B%2032%20people%20are%20still%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707650780000%2C%22vi