ata-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.democracynow.org%2F2024%2F1%2F17%2Fgaza_journalists_killed%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707517222034000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3av7a2VExL2vGo0C_P4vJ8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20DemocracyNow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CGaza%20is%20now%20the%20deadliest%20place%20on%20Earth%20for%20media%20workers.%E2%80%9D%20We%20demand%20PEN%20take%20significant%20steps%20to%20save%20lives.%20As%20this%20letter%20circulates%2C%20the%20death%20toll%20among%20Palestinian%20writers%20and%20reporters%20will%20likely%20grow.%20On%20October%2025th%20PEN%20International%20called%20for%20a%20ceasefire.%20Meanwhile%2C%20PEN%20America%20has%20remained%20silent%2C%20and%20it%20has%20become%20apparent%20to%20the%20public%20whose%20lives%20and%20voices%20matter%20to%20it%20and%20whose%20don%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPEN%20America%20continually%20perpetuates%20fascist%20nation-statehood%2C%20which%20becomes%20especially%20dangerous%20when%20the%20organization%20is%20so%20keen%20to%20define%20literary%20citizenship%20and%20freedom%20of%20speech.%20Whose%20freedom%20does%20PEN%20protect%2C%20if%20outside%20of%20press%20releases%20buried%20on%20its%20website%2C%20PEN%20has%20remained%20silent%20about%20Palestinian%20journalists%2C%20writers%2C%20and%20poets%20murdered%20by%20Israel%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOn%20January%2031%2C%20PEN%20America%20chose%20to%20platform%20Mayim%20Bialik%2C%20a%20person%20committed%20to%20the%20racist%20ideology%20of%20Zionism.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20PEN%20is%20perpetuating%20dangerous%2C%20fascist%20views%20and%20offering%20tacit%20approval%20for%20the%20Zionist%2C%20racist%20and%20genocidal%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPEN%20Members%20and%20representatives%20from%20Writers%20Against%20the%20War%20On%20Gaza%20(WAWOG)%20protested%20this%20event%20indoors.%20Among%20them%20was%20Randa%20Jarrar%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20writer%20who%20has%20done%20weeks%20of%20unpaid%20labor%20for%20PEN%20as%20an%20event%20host%2C%20organizer%2C%20and%20judge%20of%20PEN%E2%80%99s%20Open%20Book%20prize%20and%20Robert%20Bingham%20prize.%20Rather%20than%20defending%20Jarrar%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20free%20expression%2C%20PEN%20America%20violently%20dragged%20her%20out%20of%20the%20event%20by%20her%20audience%20chair%2C%20and%20threatened%20her%20with%20state%20violence%2C%20stating%20that%20if%20she%20did%20not%20silence%20herself%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Police%20Department%20would%20be%20summoned%20to%20silence%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20demand%20that%20PEN%20America%20apologize%20to%20Jarrar%20for%20these%20actions%20and%20take%20more%20concrete%20steps%20to%20support%20Palestinian%20writers%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20new%20wave%20of%20repression%2C%20retaliation%20and%20bigotry%20rippling%20through%20publishing%2C%20academia%2C%20and%20the%20creative%20arts%20industries.%20We%20demand%20PEN%20America%20create%20a%20legal%20strategy%20to%20get%20Palestinian%20authors%20and%20poets%20asylum%20immediately%2C%20and%20to%20publicize%20these%20efforts%3B%20to%20use%20its%20institutional%20power%20and%20resources%2C%20just%20as%20PEN%20does%20under%20the%20Writers%20in%20Crisis%20and%20Writers%20at%20Risk%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20demand%20PEN%20raise%20just%20as%20much%20hell%20over%20the%20unlawful%20detainment%20since%20December%2012%20of%20Mostafa%20Sheta%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Freedom%20Theater%20in%20Jenin%2C%20by%20Zionist%20occupation%20forces%2C%20as%20they%20do%20about%20those%20being%20unlawfully%20detained%20by%20states%20in%20opposition%20to%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20demand%20PEN%20find%20the%20same%20zeal%20and%20passion%20that%20they%20have%20for%20banned%20books%20in%20the%20US%20to%20speak%20out%20about%20actual%20human%20beings%20in%20Palestine.%20As%20PEN%20America%20advances%20its%20campaigns%20against%20book%20banning%20and%20freedom%20of%20speech%20on%20campuses%20throughout%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20Zionist%20occupation%20forces%20have%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%20372%20educational%20facilities%2C%20including%20every%20single%20university%20and%20the%20Gaza%20Municipal%20Library%2C%20which%20served%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F11%2F30%2Fgaza-library-palestinian-culture%2F%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F11%2F30%2Fgaza-library-palestinian-culture%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707517222034000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1yL2LtlA_V_QBJ4OJZTtvE%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultural%20center%20and%20library%20for%20children%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%20They%20are%20targeting%20artists%2C%20poets%2C%20and%20writers.%20They%20murdered%20poet%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fread-the-last-words-of-writer-heba-abu-nada-who-was-killed-last-week-by-an-israeli-airstrike%2F%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fread-the-last-words-of-writer-heba-abu-nada-who-was-killed-last-week-by-an-israeli-airstrike%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707517222034000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3yErucWStsLGk3xLxpX3C2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Heba%20Abu%20Nada%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20kidnapped%20poet%20and%20writer%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F6338183%2Fpalestinian-poet-mosab-abu-toha-arrested-gaza-israel%2F%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F6338183%2Fpalestinian-poet-mosab-abu-toha-arrested-gaza-israel%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707517222034000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3r4zE58mSdfajayDHXWhSX%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMosab%20Abu%20Toha%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Murdering%20writers%20and%20bombing%20libraries%20is%20the%20ultimate%20book%20ban.%20Destroying%20universities%20is%20the%20ultimate%20repression%20of%20campus%20free%20speech.%20Besides%20that%2C%20PEN%20America%20has%20not%20extended%20its%20campaign%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprismreports.org%2F2023%2F11%2F30%2Fpalestinian-authors-wave-of-censorship%2F%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fprismreports.org%2F2023%2F11%2F30%2Fpalestinian-authors-wave-of-censorship%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707517222035000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2lkIZ8320qyYZdt9MfKraf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20talk%20about%20censorship%20of%20Palestinian%20writers%20in%20the%20United%20States%3C%2Fa%3E.%20All%20these%20struggles%20are%20crucial%20to%20this%20time.%20But%20when%20PEN%20only%20speaks%20out%20about%20banned%20books%20here%20while%20our%20tax%20dollars%20fund%20a%20genocide%2C%20it%20deepens%20its%20complicity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20demand%20PEN%20wake%20up%20from%20its%20own%20silent%2C%20tepid%2C%20neither-here-nor-there%2C%20self-congratulatory%20middle%20of%20the%20road%20and%20take%20an%20actual%20stand%20against%20an%20actual%20genocide.%20The%20bare%20minimum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPEN%E2%80%99s%20charter%20claims%20its%20goal%20is%20%E2%80%9Cto%20dispel%20all%20hatreds%20and%20to%20champion%20the%20ideal%20of%20one%20humanity%20living%20in%20peace%20and%20equality%20in%20one%20world.%E2%80%9D%20If%20PEN%20cannot%20live%20up%20to%20its%20mission%20of%20protecting%2C%20platforming%2C%20and%20amplifying%20those%20writers%20made%20most%20marginalized%20by%20nefarious%20forces%2C%20those%20living%20under%20constant%20threat%20of%20death%20for%20simply%20telling%20the%20truth%20about%20the%20world%20they%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20inhabit%2C%20then%20PEN%20should%20disband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThere%20is%20no%20form%20of%20censorship%20more%20powerful%20than%20the%20extermination%20of%20an%20entire%20people%2C%20no%20silencing%20more%20absolute%20than%20genocide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESee%20the%20full%20list%20of%20signatories%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeOYSWhNE1tR74Qo5xw0OZ00wKauRsROVqYOw_icGBr2ybwBw%2Fviewform%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707649227000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11160244%2FGF6cP-3WEAEJ033.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2F600-writers-poets-urge-pen-america-to-do-the-bare-minimum-for-palestinian-authors%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20demand%20PEN%20wake%20up%20from%20its%20own%20silent%2C%20tepid%2C%20neither-here-nor-there%2C%20self-congratulatory%20middle%20of%20the%20road%20and%20take%20an%20actual%20stand%20against%20an%20actual%20genocide.%20The%20bare%20minimum.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2F600-writers-poets-urge-pen-america-to-do-the-bare-minimum-for-palestinian-authors%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rs%20750%20cr%20stuck%20in%20Qatar%20projects%20due%20to%20delays%20in%20payments%3A%20Voltas%20CEO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707648861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-04%2F15%2Ffull%2F1586924979-2029.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frs-750-cr-stuck-in-qatar-projects-due-to-delays-in-payments-voltas-ceo-124021100299_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MEP%20(mechanical%2C%20electrical%2C%20and%20plumbing)%20contractor%20Voltas%20has%20completed%20the%20projects%20in%20Qatar%20and%20handed%20them%20over%20as%20per%20the%20contract.%20However%2C%20its%20bills%20are%20not%20getting%20certified%20and%20paid%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frs-750-cr-stuck-in-qatar-projects-due-to-delays-in-payments-voltas-ceo-124021100299_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frs-750-cr-stuck-in-qatar-projects-due-to-delays-in-payments-voltas-ceo-124021100299_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frs-750-cr-stuck-in-qatar-projects-due-to-delays-in-payments-voltas-ceo-124021100299_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Talking%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F07131439%2FIMG_0107-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9COn%20principle%20it%20is%20quite%20wrong%20to%20try%20founding%20a%20theory%20on%20observable%20magnitude%20alone.%20In%20reality%20the%20very%20opposite%20happens.%20It%20is%20the%20theory%20which%20decides%20what%20we%20can%20observe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%88%BC%20Albert%20Einstein%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%205%2C%202024%2C%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttarakhand%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20tabled%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20Bill%20.%20The%20rather%20complex%20document%20(with%20seven%20schedules%20and%20392%20sections)%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20House%20the%20very%20next%20day.%20Uttarakhand%20thus%20becomes%20the%20first%20state%20in%20independent%20India%20to%20pass%20a%20common%20law%20on%20marriage%2C%20divorce%2C%20inheritance%20and%20even%20live-in%20relationships%20between%20two%20consenting%20adults.%20The%20hurry%20with%20which%20the%20Bill%20was%20brought%20and%20passed%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%202024%20elections%20clearly%20indicates%20a%20similar%20passage%20for%20the%20Bill%20in%20all%20other%20states%2C%20should%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20win%20with%20a%20large%20majority%2C%20of%20which%20they%20seem%20very%20sure.%20And%20when%20that%20is%20done%20we%20will%20have%20a%20pan-Indian%20civil%20society%20the%20BJP%20wishes%20to%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20293px)%2085vw%2C%20293px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22293%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22357%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20swiftly%20released%20press%20note%20from%20a%20group%20of%20Uttarakhandi%20women%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20Bill%20became%20public%2C%20the%20women%20of%20Uttarakhand%20had%20protested%20and%20rejected%20the%20draft%20in%20toto.%20According%20to%20the%20note%20which%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20disregarded%2C%20the%20Bill%20was%20built%20along%20the%20patriarchal%20Hindu%20law%20template%20and%20retained%20several%20discriminatory%20aspects%20that%20would%20deny%20women%20an%20equal%20agency%20.%20The%20leaders%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20have%20also%20protested%20over%20the%20UCC%20overtaking%20Muslim%20personal%20laws.%20The%20new%20law%20lacks%20clarity%20for%20both%20groups%20and%20that%20may%20cause%20heavy%20snarls%20when%20it%20is%20implemented.%20It%20does%20not%2C%20for%20example%2C%20distinguish%20between%20ancestral%20or%20self-acquired%20property.%20It%20seems%20to%20promote%20intrusive%20moral%20policing%20and%20may%20result%20in%C2%A0%20discriminatory%20harassment%20of%20adults%20in%20a%20relationship%20that%20has%20been%20considered%20autonomous%20and%20consensual.%20Some%20of%20the%20rules%20may%20become%20clearer%20when%20gazetted%20but%20the%20compulsory%20registration%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20is%20full%20of%20explosive%20landmines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202005%2C%20when%20the%20Hindu%20Succession%20(Amendment)%20Act%20was%20passed%20thus%20giving%20daughters%20equal%20coparcenary%20rights%20in%20ancestral%20property%2C%20the%20then%20law%20minister%20was%20asked%20by%20the%20distinguished%20lawyer%20Fali%20Nariman%20whether%20his%20government%20would%20follow%20this%20with%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20binding%20on%20all%20Indians.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20speak%20for%20all%20communities%20unless%20they%20are%20ready.%E2%80%9D%20This%20care%20for%20the%20sentiments%20and%20reservations%20among%20the%20actual%20stakeholders%20was%20mostly%20lacking%20in%20the%20preparation%20and%20the%20hasty%20passage%20of%20the%20UCC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20grassroots%20reality%2C%20was%20even%20the%20Hindu%20community%20of%20Uttarakhand%20prepped%20and%20well%20informed%20about%20the%20various%20provisions%20of%20the%20new%20law%3F%20Does%20it%20know%20that%20the%201.89%25%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20population%20has%20been%20kept%20out%20of%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20Bill%2C%20and%20has%20(according%20to%20a%20report%20based%20on%20the%20NFHS%20survey%202021)%20a%20higher%20percentage%20of%20men%20marrying%20more%20than%20one%20wife%20than%20the%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state%3F%20So%20far%20as%20one%20knows%2C%20there%20was%20no%20well%20publicised%20and%20wide%20dialogue%20between%20citizens%E2%80%99%20groups%20(especially%20the%20women%20whom%20it%20impacts%20the%20most)%20and%20the%20creators%20of%20the%20draft.%20Due%20care%20was%20also%20not%20taken%20to%20depoliticise%20the%20Bill%20by%20placing%20it%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20not%20before%20but%20after%20the%20general%20elections.%20Can%20we%20then%20pooh-pooh%20women%E2%80%99s%20groups%20and%20the%20Muslim%20minority%20seeing%20it%20as%20a%20political%20move%20to%20consolidate%20majority%20votes%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Not%20in%20the%20Name%20of%20Gender%20Justice%3A%20Reflections%20on%20Uttarakhand's%20UCC%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnot-in-the-name-of-gender-justice-reflections-on-the-uttarakhands-ucc%5C%22%3ENot%20in%20the%20Name%20of%20Gender%20Justice%3A%20Reflections%20on%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20UCC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20obvious%2C%20as%20the%20press%20note%20from%20the%20dissenting%20group%20of%20women%20says%2C%20that%20the%20State%20can%20now%20reach%20deep%20inside%20personal%20spaces%2C%20even%20invade%20the%20privacy%20of%20citizens%E2%80%99%20bedrooms.%20Supporters%20deem%20the%20UCC%20a%20progressive%20step%20that%20would%20protect%20women%20in%20live-in%20relationships%20against%20domestic%20violence%20and%20confer%20legitimacy%20and%20property%20rights%20on%20any%20children%20born%20out%20of%20wedlock.%20But%20these%20provisions%20already%20existed%20under%20the%20federal%20laws%20such%20as%20the%20Domestic%20Violence%20Act.%20And%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20already%20ruled%20that%20live-in%20relationships%20are%20not%20criminal.%20Goa%20has%20had%20a%20pre-independence%20UCC%20that%20protects%20such%20unions.%20Did%20the%20draft%20makers%20even%20consult%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20more%20unsettling%20is%20that%20the%20government%20has%20not%20only%20not%20created%20widespread%20awareness%20about%20the%20hows%20and%20whys%20about%20new%20provisions%20of%20the%20UCC%2C%20it%20has%20also%20not%20produced%20necessary%20documentation%20to%20pass%20around%20among%20citizens.%20This%20means%20that%20many%20people%2C%20especially%20the%20young%20men%20and%20women%2C%20may%20find%20that%20they%20are%20law%20violators%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20State%20because%20they%20have%20not%20submitted%20necessary%20documentation%20to%20a%20registrar%20within%2030%20days%20of%20their%20union.%20This%20failure%20may%20subject%20them%20to%20heavy%20penalties%20and%20even%20long%20jail%20sentences%2C%20without%20being%20told%20in%20clear%20terms%20how%20and%20why.%20In%20a%20state%20with%20a%20small%20but%20diverse%20population%20following%20various%20faiths%20and%20personal%20laws%2C%20with%20a%20sizeable%20rural%20population%20living%20in%20remote%20areas%2C%20any%20information%20needs%20time%20to%20reach%20and%20be%20absorbed%20by%20the%20locals.%20A%20sudden%20imposition%20of%20a%20UCC%20can%20trigger%20immediate%20and%20unforeseen%20social%2C%20political%2C%20legal%20and%20constitutional%20implications%20for%20Uttarakhandis.%20With%20the%20prolonged%20vituperative%20talk%20against%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20and%20repeated%20underlining%20in%20media%20messages%20about%20how%20the%20law%20will%20free%20Muslim%20women%20of%20%3Cem%3Ehalala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eiddat%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20bigamy%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20intent%20is%20more%20political%20than%20reformist%20and%20protective%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20intent%2C%20the%20UCC%20can%20not%20be%20faulted.%20It%20proposes%20to%20standardise%20the%20minimum%20age%20of%20marriage%20for%20all%20(already%20standardised%20for%20most%20citizens)%2C%20outlaw%20extra-judicial%20marital%20norms%20that%20exploited%20women%2C%20prohibit%20polygamy%20and%20promise%20equal%20inheritance%20to%20both%20men%20and%20women.%20Given%20how%20women%20have%20been%20exploited%20along%20these%20issues%2C%20there%20is%20no%20denying%20the%20UCC%20is%20in%20itself%20a%20good%20idea.%20But%20the%20present%20UCC%20law%20is%20full%20of%20holes.%20Take%20the%20mandatory%20registration%20(within%2030%20days)%20of%20the%20relationship%20and%20the%20punitive%20proceedings%20that%20will%20follow%20swiftly%20in%20case%20of%20failure%20to%20do%20so.%20The%20lack%20of%20public%20awareness%20about%20the%20new%20laws%20can%20easily%20hand%20the%20State%20a%20new%20tool%20and%20if%20it%20so%20desires%2C%20to%20cherry%20pick%20political%20dissenters%20and%20minorities%20to%20harass%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Centre%20opposed%20same-sex%20marriage%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20it%20did%20so%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20the%20concept%20of%20marriage%20is%20inherently%20connected%20to%20religious%20and%20cultural%20norms.%20Why%20has%20this%20autonomy%20for%20religio-cultural%20norms%20suddenly%20been%20discarded%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20registrar%20criminalising%20live-in%20relationships%20because%20the%20couple%20may%20have%20come%20to%20him%20not%20within%20the%20mandated%20period%3F%20Also%20it%20is%20unclear%20when%20couples%20go%20to%20him%20how%20he%20will%20verify%20the%20details%20provided%20by%20them.%20He%20may%20choose%20someone%20who%20can%20%E2%80%9Cconduct%20enquiry%20to%20establish%20validity%20of%20the%20relationship%E2%80%9D.%20The%20use%20of%20phrases%20to%20describe%20prohibited%20relationships%20under%20titles%20like%20%E2%80%98legitimate%20blood%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98half%20blood%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98uterine%20blood%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98full%20blood%E2%80%99%20in%20an%20actual%20legal%20document%20is%20mind%20boggling%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20Who%20can%20the%20registrar%20summon%20when%20judging%20a%20case%20of%20live-in%20relationship%3F%20An%20angry%20parent%20%3F%20A%20cousin%20with%20a%20score%20to%20settle%3F%20An%20RWA%20uncle%20who%20brought%20it%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20registrar%20who%20maintains%20the%20register%20of%20all%20such%20couples%3F%20The%20local%20Thanadhyaksh%20ji%3F%20Is%20the%20registrar%20allowed%20to%20share%20this%20register%20of%20couples%20in%20live-in%20relationship%20with%20the%20local%20police%20station%3F%20Is%20it%20a%20public%20register%20anyone%20can%20access%20like%20other%20registers%20listed%20in%20the%20new%20law%20(Part%201%2C%20Chapter%202)%20pertaining%20to%20marriages%2C%20divorces%20etc.%3F%20If%20it%20is%2C%20what%20prevents%20the%20local%20moral%20policing%20groups%20from%20intruding%20into%20the%20bedrooms%20of%20%E2%80%98suspected%E2%80%99%20citizens%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20time%20to%20recall%20that%20the%20State%20has%20not%20created%20either%20the%20institution%20of%20marriage%20or%20live-in%20relationships.%20Society%20and%20the%20changing%20times%20have.%20Each%20law%20is%20a%20society%E2%80%99s%20text%2C%20a%20reflection%20of%20its%20rational%20mind.%20But%20our%20judiciary%2C%20legislature%2C%20executive%20and%20the%20media%20are%20all%20glaringly%20minority%20and%20female%20deficient.%20So%20even%20if%20we%20believe%20in%20the%20milk%20of%20human%20kindness%20flowing%20in%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20veins%2C%20the%20State%20must%20show%20proof%20of%20its%20sincerity%20in%20recognising%20the%20enormity%20and%20complexity%20of%20the%20task%20of%20giving%20us%20a%20just%20and%20fair%20%C2%A0UCC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaakhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20Mrinal%20Pande%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20of%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%20and%20as%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F07131439%2FIMG_0107-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftalking-uniform-civil-code%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20its%20intent%2C%20the%20UCC%20can%20not%20be%20faulted.%20But%20the%20present%20Uttarakhand%20UCC%20law%20is%20full%20of%20holes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftalking-uniform-civil-code%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Boroline%20Saga%3A%20From%20a%20Symbol%20of%20the%20Swadeshi%20Movement%20to%20a%20Bengali%20Household%20Staple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11155422%2FBoroline_Antiseptic_Cream.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20August%2015%2C%201947%2C%20when%20India%20gained%20independence%20from%20British%20rule%2C%20two%20of%20Calcutta%E2%80%99s%20newspapers%20announced%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fboroline.com%2Fabout-boroline%2F%5C%22%3Eone%20lakh%20Boroline%20tubes%20would%20be%20distributed%20for%20free%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoroline%20was%20first%20launched%20in%201929%20by%20a%20Bengali%20merchant%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F173787%2Fbengal-boroline-gd-pharmaceutical-swadeshi-movement-india%2F%5C%22%3EGour%20Mohun%20Dutta.%3C%2Fa%3E%20It%20was%20then%20colloquially%20called%20%3Cem%3Ehaatiwala%3C%2Fem%3E%20cream%20(the%20cream%20with%20the%20elephant)%20because%20of%20its%20iconic%20white%20elephant%20logo%20on%20the%20green%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20product%20has%20managed%20to%20weather%20the%20eddy%20and%20flow%20of%20market%20change%20and%20is%20still%20just%20as%20relevant%20today%20as%20it%20was%2095%20years%20ago.%20Against%20all%20odds%2C%20Boroline%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20colonial%20Indian%20market%20as%20an%20effective%20and%20potent%20alternative%20to%20imported%20foreign%20creams.%20Coupled%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhomegrown.co.in%2Fhomegrown-voices%2Fswadeshi-identity-bengali-nostalgia-the-history-of-indias-first-antiseptic-cream%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Swadeshi%E2%80%99%20sentiments%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20an%20effort%20to%20promote%20India%E2%80%99s%20economic%20self-sufficiency%2C%20Boroline%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20soon%20swept%20over%20the%20entire%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20amidst%20the%20fervour%20of%20Swadeshi%20sentiments%2C%20Indians%20readily%20boycotted%20all%20foreign%20goods%20and%20embraced%20this%20multipurpose%20antiseptic%20cream%20that%20entered%20the%20market%20at%20that%20opportune%20moment%20at%20a%20cheap%20price.%20During%20the%20Second%20World%20War%2C%20G.D.%20Pharmaceutical%20sold%20the%20cream%20in%20any%20container%20available%2C%20with%20a%20label%20at%20the%20bottom%20that%20promised%2C%20%E2%80%9COriginal%20packing%20changed%20due%20to%20war%20emergency%2C%20quantity%20and%20quality%20of%20contents%20remain%20unaltered.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20small%20cut%20wounds%2C%20scabs%2C%20chapped%20and%20dried%20skin%20to%20extra%20moisturisation%20during%20chilly%20weather%20%E2%80%93%20a%20thick%20layer%20of%20Boroline%20cream%20soon%20became%20a%20one-stop%20solution%20for%20all%20skin-related%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHenceforth%2C%20the%20product%20became%20synonymous%20with%20Indian%20cultural%20identity%2C%20serving%20folks%20living%20in%20the%20cold%20Himalayan%20regions%20and%20the%20Southern%20plains%20of%20the%20country%2C%20with%20the%20same%20measure%20of%20effectiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20curious%20thing%20about%20this%20product%20is%20its%20enduring%20popularity%20against%20the%20plethora%20of%20multinational%20brands%20that%20have%20been%20flooding%20the%20market%20with%20innovative%20formulations%20every%20few%20months.%20The%20antiseptic%20formula%20of%20Boroline%20%E2%80%93%20boric%20acid%20mixed%20with%20zinc%20oxide%20%3Cem%3E(jasad%20bhasma%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20paraffin%20and%20oleum%2C%20infused%20with%20a%20unique%20fragrance%20%E2%80%93%20is%20hardly%20a%20secret.%20Yet%20a%20deluge%20of%20innovative%20skincare%20products%20and%20counterfeit%20products%20entering%20the%20market%20every%20year%20fails%20to%20dupe%20Boroline%20users%2C%20without%20any%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20for%20a%20brand%20with%20Boroline%E2%80%99s%20equity%2C%20it%20generates%20a%20yearly%20revenue%20of%20only%20Rs%20150%20crore%2C%20which%20is%20quite%20underwhelming%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FHome-Page%2FlPdtZPKn9F1l2OZogkJSoJ%2FIts-business-as-usual-for-87yearold-Boroline.html%5C%22%3ERoopen%20Roy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20former%20managing%20director%20of%20Deloitte%20Consulting%20India%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDebashish%20Dutta%2C%20grandson%20of%20Gour%20Mohun%20Dutta%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FCompanies%2FBvkIFoi2YFIY7RtiarEaRN%2FOur-thrust-will-be-on-expanding-Boroline-Suthols-retail-pe.html%5C%22%3ELivemint%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20made%20sure%20that%20our%20successful%20products%20are%20consistent%E2%80%94they%20don%E2%80%99t%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20have%20found%20that%20such%20a%20conservative%20attitude%20towards%20change%20is%20a%20common%20trait%20in%20most%20Bengali%20business%20ventures.%20They%20tend%20to%20target%20a%20very%20specific%20and%20old%20customer%20base%2C%20focusing%20more%20on%20quality%20than%20the%20numbers%20on%20the%20profit%20scale%20and%20refusing%20to%20compete%20with%20short-term%20market%20trends.%20Their%20reservation%20towards%20scaling%20up%20is%20quite%20possibly%20a%20precautionary%20response%20to%20the%20immense%20loss%20once%20incurred%20by%20the%20Bengali%20merchants%20during%20their%20trade%20with%20the%20British%20in%20the%20colonial%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20G.D.%20Pharma%E2%80%99s%202003%20launch%2C%20the%20antiseptic%20liquid%20Suthol%2C%20has%20diversified%20its%20market%20and%20is%20rapidly%20growing%20in%20popularity.%20It%20accounts%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FHome-Page%2FlPdtZPKn9F1l2OZogkJSoJ%2FIts-business-as-usual-for-87yearold-Boroline.html%5C%22%3E30%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20GD%20Pharma%E2%80%99s%20sales%20currently%2C%20showing%20remarkable%20growth%20on%20a%20year-on-year%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EG.D.%20Pharma%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20consistency%20has%20been%20equivocally%20rewarded%20by%20its%20customer%20base%2C%20even%20by%20the%20globe-trotting%20Bengali%20communities%20of%20the%20present%20day.%20Multiple%20tubs%20of%20Boroline%20go%20through%20customs%20at%20various%20airports%20every%20year%20when%20Bengalis%20move%20abroad%20for%20study%20or%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuchetana%20Chatterjee%2C%20a%20student%20living%20in%20Munich%2C%20swears%20by%20Boroline%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20tried%20tons%20of%20skincare%20products%2C%20and%20in%20-10%20degrees%2C%20nothing%20works%20as%20good%20as%20Boroline%2C%20also%20vouched%20for%20by%20some%20of%20my%20international%20friends!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShorbori%20Biswas%2C%20currently%20living%20in%20Georgia%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20use%20Boroline%20in%20Tbilisi%20as%20well%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20best%20for%20dry%20skin%20like%20mine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjini%20Mahalanobish%2C%20who%20has%20been%20living%20in%20Philadelphia%20for%20a%20few%20years%20now%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20stock%20up%20on%20%5BBoroline%5D%20on%20each%20visit%20to%20India.%20Its%20proven%20effectiveness%20and%20affordability%20make%20it%20my%20go-to%20choice%2C%20echoing%20a%20habit%20passed%20on%20by%20my%20grandparents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnwesha%20Das%2C%20a%20student%20at%20TU%20Delft%2C%20Netherlands%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20brought%20along%20five%20tubs%20to%20last%20me%20as%20long%20as%20I%20was%20away%20from%20home.%20Mum%20and%20I%20applying%20Boroline%20on%20our%20elbows%20and%20lips%20had%20been%20our%20nighttime%20ritual%20long%20before%20these%20popular%20skincare%20