itat.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20does%20the%20endgame%20of%20growth%20without%20heart%20lead%3B%20who%20benefits%20from%20%E2%80%9Cdevelopment%3B%E2%80%9D%20and%20who%20must%20pay%20its%20price%3F%20In%20how%20many%20ways%3F%20For%20how%20long%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prologue%20sets%20the%20tone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20hurts%20differently%20to%20watch%20something%20immense%20and%20majestic%20fall%20lifelessly%20to%20its%20knees%20and%20be%20taken%20apart%20by%20powers%20beyond%20its%20control.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20a%20ship%20being%20dismantled%20%E2%80%A6%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20an%20elephant%20being%20eaten%20alive%20by%20wild%20dogs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20a%20forest%20being%20mined%20and%20ravaged%20by%20corporates.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhrases%20like%20%E2%80%9Cfallout%20of%20capitalistic%20neo-imperialism%20in%20a%20globalised%20world%E2%80%9D%20get%20dismantled%2C%20and%20only%20a%20blood-splattered%20green%20silence%20of%20casual%20rape%20and%20encounter%20killings%20reverberates%20in%20the%20reader%E2%80%99s%20mind.%20The%20moral%20decay%20of%20relentless%20oppression%20is%20fleshed%20out%3A%20the%20glint%20of%20metal%20in%20pitch-dark%20jungles%2C%20sandbagged%20barriers%2C%20crumbling%20statues%20of%20%E2%80%98martyrs%2C%E2%80%99%20decrepit%20graves%20of%20comrades%2C%20faded%20red%20flags%2C%20smell%20of%20burnt%20houses.%20Images%20flash%20%E2%80%93%20a%20great%20ship%20splintering%2C%20the%20mute%20eye%20of%20an%20elephant%20being%20torn%20apart%20by%20dogs%2C%20the%20silent%20gaze%20of%20a%20sister%2C%20the%20dead%20eyes%20of%20Adivasis%20%E2%80%93%20outlining%20the%20contours%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Adivasi%20narrator%2C%20who%20had%20left%20the%20forest%20to%20pursue%20studies%2C%20later%20taking%20up%20work%20on%20a%20merchant%20navy%20ship%2C%20comes%20back%20to%20absences.%20The%20sole%20person%20who%20had%20loved%20and%20taken%20care%20of%20him%20when%20he%20was%20little%2C%20his%20stepsister%2C%20has%20joined%20the%20naxals.%20She%20is%20nowhere%20to%20be%20found%2C%20having%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cturned%20herself%20into%20the%20forest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Suspicious%20villagers%20avoid%20him%2C%20telling%20nothing.%20The%20deeper%20he%20goes%20in%2C%20the%20more%20signs%20of%20violence%20he%20encounters%2C%20witnessing%20firsthand%20how%20unequal%20violence%20and%20silence%20about%20it%2C%20scars%20bodies%20and%20psyches.%20Everyone%20%E2%80%93%20his%20school%20mates%2C%20cousins%2C%20neighbours%2C%20women%20and%20girls%20%E2%80%93%20is%20either%20a%20martyr%20and%20a%20patriot%2C%20or%20an%20outlaw%20to%20be%20hunted%20down.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIngeniously%20evil%20schemes%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Flaw-vigilante-powers-impunity%5C%22%3Esalwa%20judum%3C%2Fa%3E%20pit%20brothers%2C%20relatives%2C%20family%20members%20against%20one%20another.%20Coming%20across%20his%20own%20statue%20among%20the%20%E2%80%98martyrs%2C%E2%80%99%20makes%20him%20realise%20that%20%E2%80%9Ct%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20government%20had%20taken%20advantage%20of%20my%20own%20absence%20of%20four%20years%2C%20listed%20me%20as%20an%20SPO%20and%20declared%20me%20as%20having%20been%20killed%20by%20Naxalites.%20They%20had%20also%20perhaps%20embezzled%20the%20compensation%20money%20that%20was%20due%20to%20my%20family%20and%20dependents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20universe%20of%20corporate%20greed%20and%20State%20control%20demands%20ritual%20sacrifice%20of%20the%20Adivasis%E2%80%99%20habitat%20and%20way%20of%20life.%20He%20also%20comes%20face%20to%20face%20with%20his%20evil%20mother%20and%20witnesses%20the%20destitution%20of%20tribals%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98protected%E2%80%99%20camp.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPages%20after%20pages%20would%20be%20written%20about%20warring%20parties%2C%20but%20of%20what%20use%20would%20that%20be%3F%20Who%20would%20write%20about%20the%20people%20who%20had%20been%20ruined%20while%20they%20were%20still%20alive%3F%20Who%20would%20write%20about%20those%20adolescent%20single%20mothers%20who%20bore%20the%20illegitimate%20scions%20of%20men%20from%20the%20paramilitary%20forces%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rootedness%20and%20insularity%20of%20the%20ancient%20forests%20being%20mined%20for%20ore%2C%20contrasts%20with%20his%20ship%20that%E2%80%99s%20constantly%20on%20the%20move%2C%20ferrying%20cheap%20ore%20for%20ever-hungry%20global%20markets.%20After%20a%20brush%20with%20death%20in%20the%20jungle%2C%20the%20narrator%20leaves%20for%20the%20city%20and%20boards%20the%20ship%20again%2C%20only%20to%20find%20that%20market%20failure%20means%20that%20their%20ship%20will%20be%20dismantled%20and%20sold%20as%20scrap.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20people%20and%20their%20forests%20don%E2%80%99t%20count%2C%20nor%20does%20the%20ship%20count%3B%20only%20the%20logic%20of%20the%20market%20counts.%20A%20conversation%20with%20the%20captain%20of%20his%20ship%20leads%20the%20narrator%20to%20understand%20that%20the%20violence%20connecting%20the%20mined%20jungles%2C%20the%20Adivasis%20stripped%20of%20all%20emotion%2C%20and%20the%20ship%20slated%20to%20be%20scrapped%20is%20one%20and%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20of%20current%20times%20echoes%20the%20dark%20chapters%20of%20genocide%20from%20every%20era%20%E2%80%93%20the%20racist%20lynching%20of%20blacks%20in%20the%20US%2C%20partition%20violence%2C%20and%20the%20manmade%20cycles%20of%20drought%20and%20famine%20in%20Ethiopia%2C%20engendered%20by%20reckless%20eucalypt%20plantations%20catering%20to%20Western%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELiterary%20convictions%20shine%20as%20bright%20as%20political%20ones%20in%20this%20book.%20Without%20saying%20it%20aloud%2C%20the%20realisation%20dawns%20that%20what%20happened%20to%20the%20blacks%20in%20America%20and%20in%20Ethiopia%2C%20and%20what%20is%20happening%20to%20the%20adivasis%2C%20is%20also%20on%20its%20way%20for%20all%20of%20us.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20reading%20the%20original%20and%20the%20translation%2C%20I%20am%20struck%20by%20the%20enhanced%20readability%20achieved%20by%20judicious%20compression%2C%20restructuring%20of%20sentences%2C%20and%20cutting%20out%20repetitions%2C%20while%20staying%20in%20line%20with%20authorial%20intent.%20Both%20sensitivity%20for%20the%20source%20text%2C%20and%20a%20healthy%20respect%20for%20the%20capacities%20and%20possibilities%20of%20the%20English%20language%20are%20on%20display.%20Acting%20as%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20active%20collaborator%2C%20Shekhar%20has%20taken%20several%20aesthetic%20decisions%20that%20yield%20a%20taut%20pace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChoosing%20%3Cem%3EI%20Named%20My%20Sister%20Silence%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20the%20title%20(instead%20of%20translating%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EKale%20Adhyay%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20the%20translator%20has%20put%20the%20recurring%20motif%20of%20silence%20in%20focus.%20Likewise%2C%20the%20decision%20of%20adding%20a%20brief%20prologue%2C%20and%20of%20giving%20titles%20to%20individual%20chapters%2C%20trains%20attention%20on%20narrative%20themes.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20narrator%E2%80%99s%20interior%20monologue%20in%20the%20longish%20first%20chapter%20of%20the%20Hindi%20text%20has%20been%20compressed%20to%20foreground%20portions%20depicting%20the%20ship%E2%80%99s%20imminent%20dismantling%20in%20a%20shipyard.%20This%20tactic%20effectively%20contextualises%20the%20narrator%E2%80%99s%20memories%20about%20the%20ship%2C%20and%20connects%20the%20jungle-focused%20part%20I%20of%20the%20book%20to%20the%20ocean-focused%20part%20II%2C%20imparting%20a%20satisfying%20circularity%20to%20the%20story.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fthe-book-makes-the-call-jerry-pinto-on-the-importance-of-translations-and-experimental-reading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20Book%20Makes%20the%20Call%E2%80%99%3A%20Jerry%20Pinto%20on%20the%20Importance%20of%20Translations%20and%20Experimental%20Reading%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdaptations%2C%20cuts%2C%20interpolations%20are%20a%20given%20when%20translating%20drama%2C%20epic%20poetry%2C%20and%20songs.%20However%2C%20deviations%20from%20text%20remain%20a%20vexatious%20issue%20for%20translators%20of%20narrative%20fiction.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20Shekhar%20was%20kind%20enough%20to%20answer%20my%20questions%20on%20considerations%20that%20guided%20his%20translation%20choices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlease%20share%20why%20you%20chose%20to%20translate%20this%20novel.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20chose%20to%20translate%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKale%20Adhyay%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Einto%20English%20for%20two%20reasons.%20First%2C%20I%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20power%20of%20Manoj%20Rupda%E2%80%99s%20writing.%20After%20reading%20and%20thoroughly%20enjoying%20his%20Hindi%20story%2C%20%3Cem%3ETower%20of%20Silence%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EI%20translated%20it.%20I%20became%20a%20fan%20of%20his%20from%20that%20one%20story%20alone.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecond%2C%20because%20of%20the%20elephant%20scene%20and%20the%20character%20of%20the%20sister%2C%20Madavi%20Irma.%20There%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20third%20reason%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKale%20Adhyay%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20a%20tremendous%20book.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20make%20the%20recurring%20theme%20of%20silence%20the%20focal%20point%20by%20utilising%20it%20for%20the%20title.%20How%20does%20it%20enhance%20the%20fundamental%20meaning%20of%20the%20source%20text%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20overarching%20theme%20of%20the%20novel%2C%20%3Cem%3EKale%20Adhyay%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ekhamoshi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20silence.%20The%20literal%20translation%20of%20the%20title%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98Dark%20Chapters%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20would%20not%20have%20been%20that%20effective.%20%3Cem%3EI%20Named%20My%20Sister%20Silence%3C%2Fem%3E%20does%20not%20just%20place%20%E2%80%9Ckhamoshi%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Csilence%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20at%20the%20centre%20stage%2C%20it%20also%20gives%20the%20reader%20a%20hint%20of%20what%20they%20can%20expect%20to%20find%20in%20the%20novel.%20Also%2C%20%3Cem%3EI%20Named%20My%20Sister%20Silence%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0sounds%20intriguing%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhile%20rambling%20sentences%20add%20narrative%20emphasis%20in%20Hindi%2C%20without%20sounding%20odd%2C%20a%20good%20sentence%20in%20English%20needs%20a%20defined%20subject%20and%20is%20often%20structured%20differently.%20Please%20share%20how%20you%20go%20about%20balancing%20the%20essential%20and%20cutting%20the%20superfluous.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20something%20is%20superfluous%2C%20I%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20it%20right%20while%20translating%20the%20text.%20What%20may%20not%20sound%20rambling%20in%20the%20source%20language%2C%20may%20very%20well%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20rambling%20in%20the%20target%20language.%20So%2C%20I%20go%20by%20that%20instinct%20of%20mine%20which%20tells%20me%20that%20I%20should%20keep%20one%20thing%20while%20deleting%20the%20other.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Hindi%20novel%20uses%20words%20like%20%3Cem%3Emaan%2C%20pitaji%2C%20behan%3C%2Fem%3E%20while%20you%20replace%20these%20forms%20of%20address%20with%20%3Cem%3EKako%2C%20Buba%2C%20Yaya.%3C%2Fem%3E%20This%20certainly%20infuses%20vitality%20and%20makes%20the%20translation%20belong%20to%20its%20milieu.%20How%20did%20this%20come%20about%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EKako%2C%20Buba%2C%20Yaya%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20etc.%20are%20from%20the%20Gondi%20language%20that%20the%20Gond%20people%20(also%20known%20as%20Koitur%20or%20Koya%20people)%20speak.%20I%20needed%20to%20use%20Gondi%20words%20because%20I%20assumed%20that%20the%20people%20living%20in%20a%20village%20in%20the%20depths%20of%20a%20forest%20in%20Bastar%20would%20speak%20their%20mother%20tongue.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ERozy%20Gawde%2C%20a%20native%20Gondi%20speaker%20based%20in%20Bastar%2C%20from%20the%20Koitur%20community%20gave%20me%20these%20%5Bwords%5D%20and%20I%20cannot%20thank%20her%20enough%20for%20her%20help.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20think%20that%20the%20author%20in%20you%20is%20taking%20over%20the%20translator%2C%20when%20you%20make%20editorial%20decisions%20on%20the%20efficacy%20of%20the%20translated%20text%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAnswer%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%20certainly%20does%2C%20and%20I%20am%20happy%20about%20it.%20Since%20I%20am%20an%20author%20%E2%80%93%20and%20a%20reader%2C%20first%20and%20foremost%20%E2%80%93%20I%20know%20what%20a%20reader%20might%20expect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20a%20translator%E2%80%99s%20guilt%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETranslators%20should%20not%20feel%20guilty%20about%20modifying%20the%20translated%20text%20to%20make%20it%20more%20appealing%20and%20concise%2C%20about%20playing%20with%20the%20source%20text%20and%20working%20with%20it%20the%20way%20they%20find%20best.%20Translators%20should%20not%20feel%20guilty%20about%20not%20treating%20the%20source%20text%20with%20reverence%20(which%2C%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20is%20just%20an%20undue%20reverence).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20speak%20a%20bit%20on%20the%20considerations%20translators%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20when%20deviating%20from%20the%20source%20text%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%5BThere%20is%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20only%20one%20consideration%3A%20Do%20not%20lose%20the%20meaning%20that%20the%20original%2Fsource%20text%20wants%20to%20convey.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBased%20in%20Delhi%2C%20%3Cspan%3EVarsha%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Tiwary%20works%20as%20an%20auditor%2C%20and%20translates%20between%20Hindi%20and%20English.%20She%20also%20writes%20short%20stories%20and%20essays%2C%20which%20have%20appeared%20in%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Bombay%20Literary%20Magazine%3Cem%3E%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707642057000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F06155211%2Fvillage-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbook-review-i-named-my-sister-silence-hansda-shekhar-translation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shekhar%20suggests%20that%20a%20direct%20translation%20of%20Manoj%20Rupda%E2%80%99s%20book%2C%20'Kale%20Adhyay'%2C%20to%20'Dark%20Chapters'%2C%20might%20not%20have%20been%20as%20effective.%20He%20explains%20that%20'I%20Named%20My%20Sister%20Silence'%20provides%20readers%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20what%20to%20expect%20in%20the%20novel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbook-review-i-named-my-sister-silence-hansda-shekhar-translation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Internet%20Suspended%20in%207%20Haryana%20Districts%20as%20Farmers%20Prepare%20for%20'Delhi%20Chalo'%20Protest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F31153655%2FUntitled-design-8-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalandhar%2FChandigarh%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20scheduled%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20on%20February%2013%2C%20the%20Haryana%20government%20on%20Saturday%20evening%20announced%20the%20suspension%20of%20mobile%20internet%20services%20from%20February%2011%20to%20February%2013%20in%20Ambala%2C%20Kurukshetra%2C%20Kaithal%2C%20Jind%2C%20Hisar%2C%20Fatehabad%20and%20Sirsa%20including%20Dabwali%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20from%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20newly%20floated%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%20led%20by%20senior%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leader%20from%20the%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%20non-political%20and%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%20(KMSC)%20president%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20are%20organising%20the%20February%2013%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20order%2C%20additional%20chief%20secretary%2C%20Haryana%20government%20T.V.S.N.%20Prasad%20said%20that%20in%20view%20of%20the%20call%20for%20a%20farmers%E2%80%99%20march%2Fagitation%20given%20by%20certain%20organisations%2C%E2%80%9DThere%20is%20a%20clear%20potential%20of%20disruption%20of%20public%20utilities%2C%20damage%20to%20public%20assets%20and%20amenities%20and%20disturbance%20of%20public%20law%20and%20order%20in%20above%20mentioned%20districts%20on%20account%20of%20misuse%20of%20internet%20services%20by%20way%20of%20spread%20of%20inflammatory%20material%20and%20false%20rumours%2C%20which%20are%20being%2Fcould%20be%20transmitted%2Fcirculated%20to%20the%20public%20through%20social%20media%2Fmessaging%20services%20on%20mobile%20internet%20services%2C%20SMS%20services%20and%20other%20dongle%20services.%E2%80%9D%20All%20Haryana%20telecom%20operators%20have%20been%20directed%20to%20ensure%20compliance%20with%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20has%20been%20passed%20under%20Section%205%20of%20Indian%20Telegraph%20Act%2C%201885%20and%20Rule%202%20of%20temporary%20suspension%20of%20Telecom%20Services%20(Public%20Emergency%20or%20Public%20Safety)%20Rules%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20further%20read%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20hereby%20order%20the%20suspension%20of%20the%20mobile%20internet%20services%2C%20bulk%20SMS%20(excluding%20banking%20and%20mobile%20recharge)%20and%20all%20dongle%20services%20etc.%20provided%20on%20mobile%20networks%20except%20the%20voice%20calls%20in%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20districts%20Ambala%2C%20Kurukshetra%2C%20Kaithal%2C%20Jind%2C%20Hisar%2C%20Fatehabad%20and%20Sirsa%20of%20Haryana%20State.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20message%20on%20X%2C%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%2C%20coordinator%20and%20the%20president%20of%20KMSC%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20got%20to%20know%20from%20the%20media%20that%20the%20Haryana%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20suspend%20internet%20services%2C%20which%20is%20totally%20inhumane.%20Converting%20Haryana%20into%20an%20open%20jail%20is%20not%20good.%20This%20cannot%20be%20the%20decision%20of%20a%20democratically%20elected%20government.%20On%20one%20hand%20the%20Central%20govt%20is%20talking%20to%20farmers%20through%20the%20Punjab%20government%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20they%20are%20conducting%20raids%20and%20creating%20trouble%20for%20our%20women.%20We%20condemn%20the%20Haryana%20government%E2%80%99s%20attitude.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandher%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20appeal%20to%20the%20Haryana%20people%20and%20farmers%20that%20the%20entire%20country%20and%20Punjab%20stand%20with%20them.%20%3Cem%3EHum%20log%20peaceful%20tarike%20se%20February%2013%20ka%20protest%20karenge%2C%20jo%20%E2%80%98aar-paar%E2%80%99%20ka%20hoga%3C%2Fem%3E%20(We%20will%20lead%20the%20February%2013%20protest%20peacefully%2C%20which%20will%20be%20a%20do%20or%20die%20battle).%20We%20have%20also%20conveyed%20to%20the%20mediators%20between%20farmers%20and%20the%20Centre%20to%20ask%20the%20Haryana%20DGP%20to%20stop%20all%20that%20they%20are%20doing%20to%20target%20farmers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20internet%20ban%20order%2C%20Ranjit%20Singh%20Raju%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Gramin%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Samiti%2C%20Sri%20Ganganagar%20district%2C%20Rajasthan%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20do%20not%20need%20any%20network%20for%20their%20protest.%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20own%20network%20is%20very%20strong.%20Rather%20this%20is%20a%20congratulatory%20sign%20for%20us.%20Modi%20government%20is%20afraid%2C%20hence%20indulging%20in%20such%20tactics.%20Farmers%20will%20be%20moving%20to%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20internet%20ban%20order%20came%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20first%20round%20of%20talks%20between%20a%20delegation%20of%20the%20Central%20government%2C%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20and%20farmers%E2%80%99%20union%20leaders%2C%20who%20met%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20February%208.%20Union%20ministers%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20Arjun%20Munda%20and%20Nityanand%20Rai%20had%20assured%20the%20farmers%20that%20they%20would%20discuss%20their%20demands%20with%20the%20ministries%20concerned.%20Even%20the%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20had%20claimed%20that%20farmers%20and%20the%20government%20had%20reached%20a%20consensus%20on%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20KMM%20gave%20a%20call%20for%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20protest%2C%20farmers%20across%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20have%20been%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20march.%20Farmers%20have%20been%20gathering%20dry%20ration%20for%20six%20months%2C%20tents%2C%20beds%2C%20fans%20and%20other%20essentials%20in%20the%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20police%20has%20barricaded%20highways%20leading%20to%20Delhi%20and%20was%20also%20conducted%20late%20night%20raids%20on%20the%20houses%20of%20the%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CHaryana%20police%20are%20reaching%20our%20houses%20without%20lady%20police%20late%20at%20night%20and%20questioning%20our%20women%20about%20our%20whereabouts.%20We%20are%20being%20targeted%20just%20because%20we%20are%20raising%20our%20voice%20against%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20dictatorial%20attitude.%20The%20Modi%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20implement%20MSP%20law%2C%20justice%20to%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20victims%2C%20compensation%20to%20farmers%20martyred%20in%20farmers%20agitations%20and%20pension%20for%20their%20welfare.%20We%20will%20not%20sit%20quietly%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20farmers%E2%80%99%20union%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20some%20of%20the%20big%20farmers%E2%80%99%20unions%20including%20BKU%20Ugrahan%20and%20original%20SKM%20faction%20under%20Dr%20Darshan%20Pal%2C%20Yadvindra%20Yadav%20and%20others%20distanced%20themselves%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98Dilli%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20last%20week%2C%20SKM%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20national%20coordination%20committee%20of%20SKM%20held%20an%20online%20meeting%20and%20clarified%20that%20SKM%20has%20not%20given%20any%20call%20for%20%E2%80%98Dilli%20Chalo%E2%80%99.%20SKM%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20decision%20of%20certain%20kisan%20organisations%20to%20protest%20in%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%E2%80%99s%20SKM%20(non-political)%20faction%20believes%20that%20once%20their%20protest%20reaches%20Delhi%2C%20all%20major%20unions%20will%20join%20them%20since%20the%20issues%20they%20are%20fighting%20for%20are%20genuine%20and%20legitimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707636669000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F31153655%2FUntitled-design-8-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Finternet-suspended-in-7-haryana-districts-as-farmers-plan-for-delhi-chalo-protest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20farmers'%20groups%20have%20said%20they%20will%20march%20to%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013.%20The%20Haryana%20Police%20has%20already%20put%20