20a%20device%20to%20assist%20farmers%20in%20performing%20multiple%20tasks%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20boys%20were%20in%20Class%206%20when%20the%20pandemic%20started.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20L%26amp%3BT%20started%20providing%20online%20classes%20to%20teach%20science%2C%20arts%20and%20maths.%20The%20students%20were%20given%20easy%20ways%20to%20make%20simple%20projects%20at%20home%2C%20which%20kept%20them%20occupied%20while%20they%20learnt%20the%20important%20concepts%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thenmughil%20tells%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20despite%20facing%20challenges%20in%20writing%20Tamil%20or%20English%20proficiently%2C%20these%20boys%20exhibit%20a%20remarkable%20understanding%20of%20science%20concepts.%20They%20independently%20constructed%20the%20entire%20device%2C%20delving%20into%20areas%20of%20agriculture%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20beyond%20%E2%80%94%20showcasing%20their%20adeptness%20in%20practical%20knowledge%20and%20hands-on%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2024%20teams%20(50%20children)%20from%20Chennai%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Hazira%2C%20Vadodara%2C%20Talegaon%20and%20Mumbai%20made%20it%20to%20the%20finals%2C%20which%20was%20conducted%20in%20Mumbai%20on%203%20February%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20STEM%20activities%20around%20existing%20curriculums%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201500px)%20100vw%2C%201500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22By%20connecting%20with%20underserved%20schools%20without%20STEM%20labs%2C%20children%20in%20remote%20areas%20can%20now%20improve%20their%20scientific%20knowledge.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935.jpeg%201500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340837%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBy%20connecting%20with%20underserved%20schools%20without%20STEM%20labs%2C%20children%20in%20remote%20areas%20can%20now%20improve%20their%20scientific%20knowledge.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility%20(CSR)%20initiatives%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20has%20been%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%20education%20sector%20for%20over%20three%20decades.%20Recognising%20that%20nearly%2080%20percent%20of%20future%20jobs%20will%20require%20science%20and%20math%20skills%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20aims%20to%20address%20the%20challenge%20of%20limited%20access%20and%20resources%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMabel%20Abraham%2C%20Head%20%E2%80%93%20Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility%20at%20L%26amp%3BT%2C%20explained%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20focus%20on%20STEM%20was%20made%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL%26amp%3BT%20has%20undertaken%20a%20comprehensive%20approach%20to%20facilitate%20access%20to%20STEM%20education%20in%20government%20schools%20and%20schools%20with%20limited%20resources.%20This%20initiative%20is%20designed%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20and%20ensure%20that%20students%20have%20the%20necessary%20tools%20and%20opportunities%20to%20develop%20skills%20essential%20for%20the%20evolving%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20different%20models%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20STEM%20education%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302015%2Fboson-whitewater-bengaluru-startup-converts-stp-water-to-high-quality-potable-drinking-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20science%20labs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20implementing%20digital%20classrooms%2C%20and%20providing%20DIY%20kits%2C%20among%20other%20approaches.%20We%20did%20not%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20just%20one%20model%2C%20and%20instead%2C%20we%20decided%20on%20a%20blended%20approach%2C%20working%20to%20address%20the%20specific%20needs%20of%20each%20school%20as%20cracking%20just%20one%20piece%20of%20the%20puzzle%20is%20not%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mabel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmbracing%20the%20Smart%20School%20concept%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20initially%20focussed%20on%20furnishing%20schools%20with%20fundamental%20infrastructure%20before%20progressing%20to%20the%20establishment%20of%20STEM%20labs.%20However%2C%20their%20original%20plan%20underwent%20adjustments%20due%20to%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20pandemic%20coinciding%20with%20the%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommencing%20with%2065%20schools%20nationwide%2C%20it%20pivoted%20to%20online%20classes%20and%20modules%20in%20response%20to%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20COVID-19.%20The%20volunteers%20distributed%20WhatsApp%20videos%20and%20assigned%20children%20straightforward%20DIY%20projects%20that%20could%20be%20completed%20using%20materials%20readily%20available%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Teachers%20note%20that%20these%20models%20not%20only%20let%20students%20display%20creativity%20but%20also%20assist%20in%20delivering%20more%20effective%20explanations%2C%20using%20the%20visual%20aids%20provided%20by%20the%20projects.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969-1536x864.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340838%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETeachers%20note%20that%20these%20models%20not%20only%20let%20students%20display%20creativity%20but%20also%20assist%20in%20delivering%20more%20effective%20explanations%2C%20using%20the%20visual%20aids%20provided%20by%20the%20projects.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChildren%20were%20excited%20to%20do%20the%20projects%20and%20they%20would%20share%20it%20eagerly.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20even%20hosted%20an%20online%20science%20fair%20to%20showcase%20their%20creations.%20We%20were%20amazed%20by%20the%20projects%20they%20came%20up%20with%3B%20it%20fired%20their%20creativity%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Mabel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL%26amp%3BT%20collaborates%20with%20local%20NGO%20partners%20to%20implement%20the%20programme%20in%20selected%20schools%2C%20committing%20to%20support%20these%20schools%20for%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20years.%20The%20initiative%20works%20on%20dual%20fronts%20%E2%80%94%20providing%20training%20to%20teachers%20in%20STEM%20education%20and%20building%20physical%20infrastructure%20in%20schools%2C%20including%20STEM%20labs%20or%20digital%20classrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20begins%20with%20L%26amp%3BT%20selecting%20a%20school%2C%20and%20conducting%20an%20orientation%20and%20a%20needs%20assessment.%20A%20key%20criterion%20is%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20science%20teacher%2C%20and%20the%20initiative%20is%20tailored%20for%20students%20in%20Classes%206%20to%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20through%20NGO%20partners%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20delivers%20training%20to%20the%20district%20education%20officer%2C%20school%20principal%2C%20and%20teachers.%20Quarterly%20training%20sessions%20are%20conducted%20for%20teachers%2C%20with%20an%20observer%20present%20in%20the%20classroom%20to%20evaluate%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20teaching%20and%20provide%20guidance%20on%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20hands-on%20approach%20not%20only%20equips%20teachers%20to%20impart%20knowledge%20effectively%20but%20also%20strives%20to%20establish%20a%20sustainable%20model.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20empower%20teachers%20to%20continue%20delivering%20quality%20education%20independently%2C%20even%20without%20ongoing%20assistance%20from%20the%20NGO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20idea%20is%20to%20improve%20children%E2%80%99s%20conceptual%20understanding%20of%20science.%20Based%20on%20our%20observation%2C%20many%20students%20lose%20interest%20in%20science%20in%20Classes%206%20to%209.%20Girl%20students%20too%20face%20several%20biases%20and%20challenges%20as%20STEM%20courses%20are%20not%20traditionally%20considered%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20domain.%20If%20they%20get%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20scientific%20concepts%20through%20innovative%20methods%2C%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20of%20them%20choosing%20a%20career%20in%20science%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Mabel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdapting%20to%20the%20specific%20needs%20and%20interests%20of%20each%20school%20management%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20enhances%20the%20physical%20infrastructure%20based%20on%20demand.%20What%20started%20with%2065%20schools%20has%20now%20expanded%20to%20include%20208%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeachers%20share%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20these%20models%20not%20only%20allows%20students%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340084%2Fgujarat-school-for-the-blind-and-visually-impaired-inclusive-design-architecture-by-anand-sonecha-sealabs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshowcase%20their%20creativity%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20also%20aids%20teachers%20in%20delivering%20more%20effective%20explanations%2C%20utilising%20the%20visual%20aids%20provided%20by%20the%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20we%20would%20just%20explain%20concepts%2C%20with%20children%20not%20being%20able%20to%20see%20how%20it%20works.%20Through%20these%20models%20and%20kits%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20demonstrate%20how%20the%20concept%20works%2C%20helping%20in%20easier%20understanding.%20Children%20also%20ask%20more%20questions.%20The%20concept%20reaches%20them%20easily%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Veeramuthu%20N%2C%20a%20teacher%20from%20Government%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%2C%20Kaliannanpudur%2C%20Coimbatore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20L%26amp%3BT%20has%20provided%20them%20with%2075%20kits%2C%20which%20include%20working%20models%2C%20explanatory%20models%20and%20charts.%20Children%20are%20taken%20to%20the%20lab%2C%20where%20they%20can%20experiment.%20Alternatively%2C%20teachers%20also%20bring%20the%20models%20to%20class%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20concept%20they%20are%20teaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20NGO%20partners%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20American%20India%20Foundation%20(AIF)%20and%20Don%20Bosco%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20%E2%80%94%20offer%20after-school%20classes%20for%20students.%20These%20sessions%20cover%20a%20range%20of%20topics%2C%20including%20mobile%20application%20development%2C%20coding%2C%20CNC%20machining%2C%20sensors%2C%20map%20making%2C%203D%20printing%2C%20and%20more.%20The%20knowledge%20gained%20in%20these%20classes%20empowers%20children%20to%20apply%20these%20concepts%20to%20solve%20real-life%20problems%20they%20encounter%20in%20their%20daily%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFiring%20the%20creativity%20in%20children%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203121913-1-min-1707141250-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20winners%20made%20an%20agricultural%20tricyle%20using%20scrap%20materials%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203121913-1-min-1707141250-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203121913-1-min-1707141250-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203121913-1-min-1707141250-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203121913-1-min-1707141250-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203121913-1-min-1707141250-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203121913-1-min-1707141250-1536x1536.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203121913-1-min-1707141250-2048x2048.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203121913-1-min-1707141250-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340840%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20winners%20made%20an%20agricultural%20tricycle%20using%20scrap%20materials.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20boost%20the%20initiative%20and%20provide%20students%20with%20a%20platform%20to%20showcase%20their%20talents%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20initiated%20STEM%20fests%20beginning%20in%20October%202023.%20Over%206%2C000%20students%20from%20Classes%206%20to%209%20actively%20participated%20in%20intra%20and%20inter-school%20level%20competitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20STEM%20model-making%20competition%20featured%20interesting%20themes%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20green%20and%20sustainable%20energy%2C%20waste%20management%2C%20smart%20schools%2C%20and%20satellite%20and%20launch%20vehicles.%20From%20these%20themes%2C%20208%20teams%20were%20selected%20for%20the%20regional%20level%20competition%2C%20and%20ultimately%2C%2024%20teams%20from%20cities%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Chennai%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Hazira%2C%20Vadodara%2C%20Talegaon%2C%20and%20Mumbai%20%E2%80%94%20advanced%20to%20the%20finale%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL%26amp%3BT%E2%80%99s%20employee%20volunteers%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20mentoring%20and%20assisting%20students%2C%20helping%20them%20refine%20and%20perfect%20their%20models%20for%20the%20competitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20High%20School%2C%20Gerugambakkam%2C%20Chennai%2C%20won%20the%20challenge%2C%20while%20the%20Government%20High%20School%2C%20Velappanchavudi%2C%20Chennai%20and%20Shree%20Kanchanlal%20Mamawala%20Surat%20Municipal%20Corporation%20School%20(Hazira%2C%20Gujarat)%20emerged%20as%20the%20first%20and%20second%20runners-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20winning%20schools%20received%20cash%20rewards%20%E2%80%94%20Rs%2050%2C000%20for%20the%20national%20champion%2C%20Rs%2030%2C000%20for%20the%20first%20runner-up%2C%20and%20Rs%2020%2C000%20for%20the%20second%20runner-up%20%E2%80%94%20to%20facilitate%20the%20upgrading%20of%20their%20science%20labs.%20Additionally%2C%20all%20three%20winning%20teams%20were%20presented%20with%20telescopes%2C%20drones%20and%20a%20DIY%20Robotics%20Kit%2C%20providing%20them%20with%20further%20exposure%20to%20STEM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20special%20opportunity%2C%20the%20winning%20teams%20were%20invited%20to%20visit%20L%26amp%3BT%E2%80%99s%20tech%20projects%20and%20engage%20in%20interactions%20with%20the%20leadership%20team%2C%20enriching%20their%20understanding%20and%20appreciation%20of%20real-world%20applications%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20block%20level%20coding%20workshop%20organised%20by%20AIF%2C%20Class%207%20students%20%E2%80%94%20Santhosh%20M%20and%20Yuvan%20Shankar%20Raja%20K%20from%20Government%20High%20School%2C%20Velappanchavadi%2C%20Chennai%20%E2%80%94%20tackled%20the%20topic%20of%20waste%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20modern%20waste%20segregating%20system%20made%20by%20students%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-1536x1536.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-2048x2048.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340839%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20modern%20waste%20segregating%20system%20made%20by%20students.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20developed%20a%20modern%20waste%20segregating%20system%20featuring%20sensors%20on%20each%20bin%20%E2%80%94%20designated%20for%20biodegradable%2C%20non-biodegradable%2C%20and%20e-waste.%20These%20sensors%20guide%20users%20on%20the%20appropriate%20bin%20for%20their%20waste%20disposal.%20Their%20innovative%20approach%20involves%20attaching%20sensors%20and%20cameras%20to%20each%20bin%2C%20aiming%20to%20facilitate%20waste%20separation%20at%20the%20source.%20Biodegradable%20waste%20is%20intended%20for%20composting%2C%20while%20non-biodegradable%20waste%20is%20directed%20towards%20recycling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20only%20nine%20percent%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325564%2Fthe-disposal-company-bhagyashree-bhansali-waste-plastic-credit-recycle-mumbai-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20is%20recycled%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20implemented%2C%20our%20invention%20can%20increase%20the%20waste%20recycled%20and%20prevent%20baby%20sea%20turtles%20from%20having%20plastic%20in%20their%20stomachs%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Santhosh%2C%20one%20of%20the%20finalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20a%20farming%20background%2C%20Apurva%20Shirsat%20and%20Kausar%20Pathan%20of%20the%20Tulshet%20Pada%20Marathi%20Medium%20School%20have%20innovated%20a%20farm%20protector%2C%20which%20uses%20two%20different%20types%20of%20sensors%20to%20ensure%20farm%20safety%20without%20harming%20animals.%20Furthermore%2C%20Gowtham%20and%20Vijay%20Darshan%20%E2%80%94%20belonging%20to%20a%20hilly%20area%20with%20just%20one%20bus%20in%20the%20morning%20%E2%80%94%20built%20a%20hydroelectric%20generator%20that%20can%20solve%20the%20problem%20of%20electricity%20using%20waste%20water%20collected%20dur