4%2F02%2Fmansi-5-1706796999-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340564%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETravellers%20with%20disabilities%20%E2%80%93%20Parvinder%20(left)%20and%20Priti%20(right).%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20terms%20of%20logistics%2C%20Parvinder%20stresses%20the%20importance%20of%20being%20prepared%20for%20various%20situations.%20%E2%80%9CUnderstanding%20your%20body%20and%20its%20needs%20is%20crucial.%20Carry%20medicines%20and%20necessary%20equipment%20without%20fail%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBefore%20travelling%20to%20a%20new%20country%2C%20she%20advises%20you%20to%20make%20sure%20you%20do%20your%20research.%20%E2%80%9CI%20thoroughly%20examine%20every%20aspect%20%E2%80%94%20scrutinising%20the%20hotel%2C%20the%20country%20itself%2C%20and%20its%20wheelchair%20accessibility.%20It%E2%80%99s%20essential%20to%20call%20the%20hotel%20or%20homestay%20in%20advance%20to%20confirm%20if%20they%20are%20fully%20equipped%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20a%20wheelchair%20user.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENo%20time%20like%20the%20present%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20such%20inspiring%20traveller%20who%20is%20on%20a%20unique%20mission%20to%20navigate%20the%20Ganga%20River%20in%20100%20days!%20A%20patient%20with%20rheumatoid%20arthritis%20with%20very%20little%20mobility%20in%20his%20fingers%20and%20left%20leg%2C%20Rency%20Thomas%20feels%20a%20sense%20of%20urgency%20with%20his%20condition%20and%20advises%20not%20to%20hesitate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20easy%20for%20people%20facing%20similar%20conditions%20like%20mine%20to%20lose%20heart%20and%20stop%20living.%20But%20I%20want%20to%20convey%20that%20it%20is%20possible.%20Whatever%20you%E2%80%99re%20dreaming%2C%20if%20you%20push%20yourse